"For more information on setting up and configuring the :guilabel:`Barcode` "
"app, refer to the :doc:`Set up your barcode scanner <../setup/hardware>` "
"and :doc:`Activate the Barcodes in Odoo <../setup/software>` docs."
msgstr ""

