#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/inventory_valuation/inventory_valuation_config.rst:81
msgid ""
"After :ref:`enabling inventory valuation <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"accounting-setup>`, the next step is to set the product category to use "
