":guilabel:`Inventory Valuation` nastavite polje :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Valuation` na :guilabel:`Automated`. Ponovite ta korak za vsako kategorijo "
"izdelka, ki namerava uporabljati samodejno vrednotenje zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/inventory_valuation/inventory_valuation_config.rst:90
msgid ""
"After enabling automatic accounting, each new stock move layer (SVL), that "
