"Poleg tega je mogoče v :guilabel:`Bilanco stanja` dodati opombe tako, da "
"izberete :guilabel:`Dodaj opombo`, izpolnite besedilno polje in kliknete "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/inventory_valuation/inventory_valuation_config.rst:None
