"Click the :guilabel:`Create` button to create the putaway rule. In "
"the :guilabel:`Having Category` field of the new putaway rule form, select "
"the storage category."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:151
