#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:53
msgid ""
"Configure removal strategies on the location by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Locations`, and selecting "
"the desired location. On the location form, choose a removal strategy from "
"the :guilabel:`Removal Strategy` field's drop-down menu options."
msgstr ""
"Strategije odvzema konfigurirajte na lokaciji tako, da "
"odprete :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Lokacije` in izberete "
"želeno lokacijo. Na obrazcu lokacije izberite strategijo odvzema iz "
"spustnega menija v polju :guilabel:`Strategija odvzema`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:58
msgid ""
"To set a removal strategy on a location, the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` "
"and :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` settings **must** be enabled "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev strategije odvzema na lokaciji **morata** biti omogočeni "
"nastavitvi :guilabel:`Skladiščne lokacije` in :guilabel:`Večstopenjske poti` "
"v :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:62
msgid ""
"These features are **only** necessary when setting the removal strategy on a "
"location."
msgstr ""
"Te funkcije so potrebne **samo** pri nastavljanju strategije odvzema na "
"mestu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:64
msgid ""
"Configure removal strategies on product categories by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Product Categories` and "
"selecting the intended product category. Next, choose a removal strategy "
"from the :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy` drop-down menu options."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte strategije odvzema na kategorijah izdelkov tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Kategorije izdelkov` in "
"izberete želeno kategorijo izdelka. Nato izberite strategijo odvzema iz "
"spustnega menija :guilabel:`Vsiljena strategija odvzema`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:69
msgid ""
"When there are different removal strategies applied on both the location and "
"product category for a product, the value set on the :guilabel:`Force "
"Removal Strategy` field set on a :guilabel:`Product Category` form is "
"applied as top priority."
msgstr ""
"Ko so različne strategije odvzema uporabljene tako na mestu kot na "
"kategoriji izdelka za izdelek, se kot najvišja prednost uporabi vrednost, "
"nastavljena v polju :guilabel:`Vsiljena strategija odvzema`, ki je "
"nastavljena na obrazcu :guilabel:`Kategorija izdelka`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies.rst:74
