#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:67
msgid ""
"To see how the closest location removal strategy works, consider the "
"following example, featuring the popular product, `iPhone charger`, which is "
"stored in `WH/Stock/Shelf 1`, `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`, and `WH/Stock/Shelf 3`."
msgstr ""
"Za razumevanje delovanja strategije odstranjevanja najbližje lokacije si "
"oglejte naslednji primer s priljubljenim izdelkom `polnilnik za iPhone`, ki "
"je shranjen v `WH/Stock/Shelf 1`, `WH/Stock/Shelf 2` in `WH/Stock/Shelf 3`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:71
msgid ""
"Fifteen, five, and thirty units are in stock at each respective location."
msgstr "Patnáct, pět a třicet jednotek je skladem na každé příslušné lokaci."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:74
msgid ""
"To check the on-hand stock at each storage location, navigate to the product "
"form, and click the :guilabel:`On Hand` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Za preverjanje zaloge na vsaki lokaciji skladiščenja pojdite na obrazec "
"izdelka in kliknite pametno gumb :guilabel:`Na zalogi`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:0
msgid "Show on-hand stock at all locations."
msgstr "Prikaži razpoložljivo zalogo na vseh lokacijah."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:81
msgid ""
"Create a :ref:`delivery order <inventory/delivery/one-step>` for eighteen "
"units of the `iPhone charger` by navigating to the :menuselection:`Sales "
"app` and creating a new quotation."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite :ref:`naročilo za dostavo <inventory/delivery/one-step>` za "
"osemnajst enot `polnilnika za iPhone` tako, da pojdete v "
":menuselection:`Aplikacijo Prodaja` in ustvarite novo ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:84
msgid ""
"After adding the products, clicking :guilabel:`Confirm` creates a delivery "
"order that reserves items stored at the closest location, using the removal "
"strategy."
msgstr ""
"Po dodajanju izdelkov klik na :guilabel:`Potrdi` ustvari dobavnico, ki "
"rezervira artikle, shranjene na najbližji lokaciji, s pomočjo strategije "
"odstranjevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:87
msgid ""
"For more details about *where* the units were picked, select "
"the :guilabel:`⦙≣ (bulleted list)` icon, located on the far-right. Doing so "
"opens the :guilabel:`Open: Stock move` pop-up window that displays how the "
"reserved items were picked, according to the removal strategy."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti o tem, *kje* so bile enote pobrane, izberite ikono "
":guilabel:`⊙≣ (seznam z alinejami)`, ki se nahaja na desni strani. S tem se "
"odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Odpri: Premik zaloge`, ki prikazuje, kako so "
"bili rezervirani artikli pobrani v skladu s strategijo odstranjevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:91
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Open: Stock move` pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Pick from` "
"field displays where the quantities to fulfill the :guilabel:`Demand` are "
"picked. All fifteen of the units stored at the closest location, `WH/Stock/"
"Shelf 1`, are picked first. The remaining three units are then selected from "
"the second closest location, `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Odpri: Premik zaloge` polje :guilabel:`Poberi iz` "
"prikazuje, od kod so pobrane količine za izpolnitev "
":guilabel:`Povpraševanja`. Najprej je pobranih vseh petnajst enot, "
"shranjenih na najbližji lokaciji `WH/Stock/Shelf 1`. Preostale tri enote so "
"nato izbrane z druge najbližje lokacije `WH/Stock/Shelf 2`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:None
msgid "Display *Pick From* quantities for the order for iPhone chargers."
msgstr "Prikaz količin *Poberi iz* za naročilo polnilnikov za iPhone."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:3
msgid "FEFO removal"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje FEFO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *First Expired, First Out* (FEFO) removal strategy targets products for "
"removal based on their assigned removal dates."
msgstr ""
"Strategija odstranjevanja *First Expired, First Out* (FEFO) izbira izdelke "
"za odstranitev na podlagi dodeljenih datumov odstranitve."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:14
msgid "Removal date"
msgstr "Datum odstranitve"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:16
msgid ""
"Products **must** be removed from inventory before their *removal date*, "
"which is set as a certain number of days before the product's *expiration "
"date*."
msgstr ""
"Izdelke je **treba** odstraniti iz zaloge pred njihovim *datumom "
"odstranitve*, ki je določen kot določeno število dni pred *datumom poteka* "
"izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:19
msgid ""
"The user sets this number of days by navigating to the product "
"form's :guilabel:`Inventory` tab. Under the :guilabel:`Traceability` "
"section, ensure the :guilabel:`Tracking` field is set to "
"either :guilabel:`By Lots` or :guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number`."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik to število dni nastavi tako, da se pomakne na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Zaloga` v obrazcu izdelka. V "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Sledljivost` zagotovite, da je "
"polje :guilabel:`Sledenje` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Po serijah` "
"ali :guilabel:`Po unikatni serijski številki`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:23
msgid ""
"Next, select the :guilabel:`Expiration Date` option, which makes "
"the :guilabel:`Removal Date` field (and other date fields) appear."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite možnost :guilabel:`Datum poteka`, kar povzroči, da se prikaže "
"polje :guilabel:`Datum odstranitve` (in druga polja za datume)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:27
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Lots and Serial Numbers` and :guilabel:`Expiration Dates` "
"features **must** be enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` to track expiration dates."
msgstr ""
"Funkciji :guilabel:`Serije in serijske številke` in :guilabel:`Datumi "
"poteka` **morata** biti omogočeni v :menuselection:`Aplikacija Zaloga --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, da lahko sledite datumom poteka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:31
msgid ""
"The expiration date of a product is determined by adding the date the "
"product was received to the number of days specified in "
"the :guilabel:`Expiration Date` field of the product form."
msgstr ""
"Datum poteka izdelka se določi tako, da datumu prejema izdelka prištejemo "
"število dni, navedeno v polju :guilabel:`Datum poteka` v obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:34
msgid ""
"The removal date takes this expiration date, and subtracts the number of "
"days specified in the :guilabel:`Removal Date` field of the product form."
msgstr ""
"Datum odstranitve vzame ta datum poteka in odšteje število dni, navedeno v "
"polju :guilabel:`Datum odstranitve` v obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:38
msgid ""
":doc:`Expiration dates <../../product_management/product_tracking/"
"expiration_dates>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Datumi poteka <../../product_management/product_tracking/"
"expiration_dates>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:41
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of the product, `Egg`, the "
"following :guilabel:`Dates` are set by the user:"
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Zaloga` izdelka `Jajce` uporabnik nastavi "
"naslednje :guilabel:`Datume`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Expiration Date`: `30` days after receipt"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum poteka`: `30` dni po prejemu"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Removal Date`: `15` days before expiration date"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum odstranitve`: `15` dni pred datumom poteka"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:None
msgid "Display expiration and removal dates set on the product form."
msgstr "Prikaz datumov poteka in odstranitve, nastavljenih v obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:51
msgid ""
"A shipment of Eggs arrive at the warehouse on January 1st. So, the "
"expiration date of the Eggs is **January 31st** (Jan 1st + 30). By "
"extension, the removal date is **January 16th** (Jan 31 - 15)."
msgstr ""
"Pošiljka jajc prispe v skladišče 1. januarja. Torej je datum poteka jajc "
"**31. januar** (1. jan + 30). Posledično je datum odstranitve **16. januar** "
"(31. jan - 15)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:57
msgid ""
"To view the expiration dates of items in stock, navigate to the product "
"form, and click the :guilabel:`On Hand` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled datumov poteka artiklov na zalogi pojdite na obrazec izdelka in "
"kliknite pametno gumb :guilabel:`Na zalogi`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:60
msgid ""
"Next, click the additional options icon, located on the far-right, and "
"select the columns: :guilabel:`Expiration Date` and :guilabel:`Removal Date`."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite ikono dodatnih možnosti na desni strani in izberite stolpce: "
":guilabel:`Datum poteka` in :guilabel:`Datum odstranitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:None
msgid ""
"Show expiration dates from the inventory adjustments model accessed from the "
"*On Hand*\n"
"smart button from the product form."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz datumov poteka iz modela prilagoditev zaloge, do katerega dostopate "
"prek pametnega gumba *Na zalogi* na obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:71
msgid ""
"Using the :abbr:`FEFO (First Expired, First Out)` removal strategy ensures "
"that products with the nearest removal date are picked first."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba strategije odstranjevanja :abbr:`FEFO (First Expired, First Out)` "
"zagotavlja, da so najprej izbrani izdelki z najbližjim datumom odstranitve."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:74
msgid ""
"To understand how this removal strategy works, consider the following "
"example below about the product, `Carton of eggs`, which is a box containing "
"twelve eggs."
msgstr ""
"Za razumevanje delovanja te strategije odstranjevanja si oglejte naslednji "
"primer o izdelku `Karton jajc`, ki je škatla z dvanajstimi jajci."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:77
msgid ""
"The product is tracked :guilabel:`By Lots`, and the product "
"category's :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy` is set to :guilabel:`First "
"Expired, First Out (FEFO)`."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek se sledi :guilabel:`Po serijah`, strategija :guilabel:`Vsili "
"strategijo odstranjevanja` kategorije izdelka pa je nastavljena na "
":guilabel:`Najprej potečeno, najprej ven (FEFO)`."

