"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab of the :guilabel:`New "
"Shipping Method` form, click on the :guilabel:`Load your SendCloud shipping "
"products` link."
msgstr ""
"Na kartě :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` formuláře :guilabel:`Nová "
"metoda přepravy` klikněte na odkaz :guilabel:`Load your SendCloud shipping "
"products`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:165
msgid ""
"Select the shipping products the company would like to use for deliveries "
