"sales orders (SOs) and used to compute delivery costs and print shipping "
"labels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:54
msgid ""
"Open or create a new shipping method. Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory "
"--> Configuration --> Shipping Methods`, then open an existing USPS shipping "
"method to display its form. Alternatively, click :guilabel:`New` to open a "
"blank form and configure a new shipping method."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:None
msgid "The USPS Domestic shipping method, fully configured."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:62
msgid ""
"Enabling the USPS shipping connector automatically creates two default "
"shipping methods: :guilabel:`USPS Domestic` and :guilabel:`USPS "
"International`. Each of these methods is preconfigured with test "
"credentials, allowing them to be used for testing purposes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:66
