msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Generate Return Label`: Samo za domače pošiljke. Izberite to "
"potrditveno polje, da se pri potrditvi dobave samodejno ustvari nalepka za "
"vračilo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:122
msgid "Turn on the USPS integration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:124
msgid ""
"After the USPS connection is set up, use the smart buttons at the top of the "
"form to publish, turn on production mode, or activate debug logging."
msgstr ""
"Ko je povezava USPS vzpostavljena, uporabite pametne gumbe na vrhu obrazca "
"za objavo, vklop produkcijskega načina ali aktivacijo beleženja "
"razhroščevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unpublished` / :guilabel:`Published`: Determines if this shipping "
