"search results that appear in the resulting pop-up window, "
"choose :guilabel:`Settings / Technical / Reporting / Reports` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Reports` page."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek prilagajanja Zebra nalepke v Odoo vklopite :ref:`razvijalski "
"način <developer-mode>` in na glavni nadzorni plošči Odoo vnesite `Reports`. "
"Iz rezultatov iskanja, ki se prikažejo v pojavnem oknu, "
"izberite :guilabel:`Nastavitve / Tehnično / Poročanje / Poročila`, da "
"odprete stran :guilabel:`Poročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:34
