#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:0
msgid ""
"Example barcode label with the product name margin adjusted to the left."
msgstr ""
"Primer nalepke s črtno kodo, kjer je rob imena izdelka prilagojen levo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:135
msgid "Resize barcode"
msgstr "Spremeni velikost črtne kode"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:137
msgid ""
"To adjust the size of the barcode to scale, begin by navigating to "
"the :ref:`ZPL code of the label <inventory/shipping_receiving/zpl-view>` in "
"the :guilabel:`Architecture` tab. Look for the `^FO` command (typically in "
"the third line), which is the starting point of the margin for the barcode."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi velikost črtne kode, najprej pojdite do :ref:`kode ZPL "
"nalepke <inventory/shipping_receiving/zpl-view>` v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Architecture`. Poiščite ukaz `^FO` (običajno v tretji "
"vrstici), ki je začetna točka roba za črtno kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:141
msgid ""
"The `^BY` command configures barcode size, and takes three numbers: bar "
"width, width of wide bars relative to narrow bars, and bar height. By "
"default, |ZPL| code in Odoo uses `^BY3`, setting the bar width to three "
"dots, a typical size that is easy for barcode scanners to read."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz `^BY` konfigurira velikost črtne kode in sprejme tri številke: širino "
"črte, širino širokih črt glede na ozke črte in višino črte. Privzeto koda |"
"ZPL| v Odoo uporablja `^BY3`, kar nastavi širino črte na tri pike, tipično "
"velikost, ki jo čitalniki črtnih kod lahko zlahka preberejo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:146
msgid "To shrink the barcode to scale, `^BY3` is reduced to `^BY2`."
msgstr "Za zmanjšanje črtne kode na merilo se `^BY3` zmanjša na `^BY2`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:0
msgid "Example barcode label."
msgstr "Primer nalepke s črtno kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:0
msgid "Example barcode label with the barcode size reduced."
msgstr "Primer nalepke s črtno kodo z zmanjšano velikostjo črtne kode."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:185
msgid "Rotate elements"
msgstr "Zavrti elemente"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:187
msgid ""
"To rotate elements in |ZPL|, begin by navigating to the :ref:`ZPL code of "
"the label <inventory/shipping_receiving/zpl-view>` in "
"the :guilabel:`Architecture` tab."
msgstr ""
"Za vrtenje elementov v |ZPL| najprej odprite :ref:`kodo ZPL nalepke "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/zpl-view>` na zavihku :guilabel:`Arhitektura`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:190
msgid ""
"The `^BC` command's first parameter (:dfn:`information that affects the "
"behavior of the command`) defines the rotation of an item, which can be:"
msgstr ""
"Prvi parameter ukaza `^BC` (:dfn:`informacija, ki vpliva na obnašanje "
"ukaza`) določa rotacijo elementa, ki je lahko:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:193
msgid "`N`: display normally"
msgstr "`N`: prikaži normalno"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:194
msgid "`R`: rotate 90 degrees"
msgstr "`R`: zavrti za 90 stopinj"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:195
msgid "`I`: rotate 180 degrees"
msgstr "`I`: zavrti za 180 stopinj"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:196
msgid "`B`: rotate 270 degrees"
msgstr "`B`: zavrti za 270 stopinj"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:199
msgid "To rotate the barcode, `^BCN` is changed to `^BCB`."
msgstr "Za vrtenje črtne kode se `^BCN` spremeni v `^BCB`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:0
msgid "Example barcode label with the barcode rotated."
msgstr "Primer nalepke s črtno kodo z obrnjeno črtno kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage.rst:5
msgid "Warehouses and storage"
msgstr "Skladišča in skladiščenje"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:6
msgid "Inventory management"
msgstr "Upravljanje zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:8
msgid ""
"In the Odoo *Inventory* app, :doc:`warehouses <inventory_management/"
"warehouses>` handle the broader organization and distribution of stock "
"across different physical sites, while :doc:`locations <inventory_management/"
"use_locations>` provide a more detailed breakdown within each warehouse for "
"efficient item management."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji Odoo *Zaloga* :doc:`skladišča <inventory_management/"
"warehouses>` upravljajo širšo organizacijo in distribucijo zaloge na "
"različnih fizičnih lokacijah, medtem ko :doc:`lokacije <inventory_management/"
"use_locations>` zagotavljajo podrobnejšo razdelitev znotraj posameznega "
"skladišča za učinkovito upravljanje izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:13
msgid ""
"This document serves as an introduction to the terminology and concepts "
"necessary to master *Inventory*. For specific instructions and examples of "
"how things work, refer to individual documentation pages."
msgstr ""
"Ta dokument je uvod v terminologijo in koncepte, potrebne za obvladovanje "
"aplikacije *Zaloga*. Za posebna navodila in primere delovanja si oglejte "
"posamezne strani dokumentacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:18
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Warehouses & Locations <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=zMvudZVLuUo>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo vodniki: Skladišča in lokacije <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=zMvudZVLuUo>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:21
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:33
msgid "Warehouses"
msgstr "Skladišča"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:23
msgid ""
":doc:`Warehouses <inventory_management/warehouses>` represent a physical "
"place, with a physical address, where a company's items are stored."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Skladišča <inventory_management/warehouses>` predstavljajo fizični "
"prostor s fizičnim naslovom, kjer so shranjeni izdelki podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:26
msgid ""
"Configure :doc:`routes <../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes>` "
"in a warehouse to control how products move to customers, from vendors, "
"within the warehouse, or :doc:`between warehouses <replenishment/"
"resupply_warehouses>`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte :doc:`poti <../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"use_routes>` v skladišču za nadzor nad tem, kako se izdelki premikajo do "
"kupcev, od dobaviteljev, znotraj skladišča ali :doc:`med skladišči "
"<replenishment/resupply_warehouses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:3
msgid "Locations"
msgstr "Lokacije"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:33
msgid ""
":doc:`Locations <inventory_management/use_locations>` refer to specific "
"areas within a warehouse, such as shelves, floors, or aisles. These are sub-"
"divisions within a warehouse, and are unique to that warehouse. Users can "
"create and manage numerous locations within a single warehouse to organize "
"inventory more precisely."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Lokacije <inventory_management/use_locations>` se nanašajo na "
"specifična območja znotraj skladišča, kot so police, nadstropja ali hodniki. "
"To so pododdelki znotraj skladišča in so edinstveni za to skladišče. "
"Uporabniki lahko ustvarijo in upravljajo številne lokacije znotraj "
"posameznega skladišča za bolj natančno organizacijo zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:39
msgid ":doc:`inventory_management/use_locations`"
msgstr ":doc:`inventory_management/use_locations`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:40
msgid ":doc:`inventory_management/count_products`"
msgstr ":doc:`inventory_management/count_products`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:41
msgid ":doc:`inventory_management/cycle_counts`"
msgstr ":doc:`inventory_management/cycle_counts`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:42
msgid ":doc:`inventory_management/scrap_inventory`"
msgstr ":doc:`inventory_management/scrap_inventory`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:47
msgid "Location types"
msgstr "Vrste lokacij"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:49
msgid ""
"*Location types* in Odoo help categorize and manage where products are, and "
"what actions need to be taken with them. By default, on "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations` page, "
"only internal locations are displayed."
msgstr ""
"*Vrste lokacij* v Odoo pomagajo kategorizirati in upravljati, kje so izdelki "
"in kakšna dejanja je treba izvesti z njimi. Privzeto so na "
"strani :menuselection:`aplikacija Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Lokacije` "
"prikazane samo notranje lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:53
msgid ""
"To view the seven location types in Odoo, select any location, and in "
"the :guilabel:`Location Type` field, there are:"
msgstr ""
"Za ogled sedmih vrst lokacij v Odoo izberite katerokoli lokacijo in v "
"polju :guilabel:`Vrsta lokacije` so:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Vendor Location`: defines an area where products purchased from "
"vendors originate. Items here are **not** in stock."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lokacija dobavitelja`: določa območje, od koder izvirajo izdelki, "
"kupljeni pri dobaviteljih. Izdelki tukaj **niso** na zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`View`: used to organize and structure the warehouse hierarchy. "
"For example, the view location `WH` (short for warehouse) groups all "
"internal locations, such as `Stock`, receiving docks, quality checkpoints, "
"and packing areas to show they all belong to the same warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pogled`: uporablja se za organiziranje in strukturiranje "
"hierarhije skladišča. Na primer, lokacija pogleda `WH` (kratica za "
"warehouse) združuje vse notranje lokacije, kot so `Stock`, območja za "
"sprejem, kontrolne točke kakovosti in območja za pakiranje, da pokaže, da "
"vse pripadajo istemu skladišču."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:64
msgid ""
"View locations should **not** contain products, but it is possible to move "
"them there."
msgstr ""
"Lokacije pogleda **ne smejo** vsebovati izdelkov, vendar jih je mogoče tja "
"premakniti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Internal Location`: storage locations within the warehouse. Items "
"stored in these locations are accounted for in :doc:`inventory valuation <../"
"product_management/inventory_valuation/using_inventory_valuation>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Notranja lokacija`: lokacije za shranjevanje znotraj skladišča. "
"Izdelki, shranjeni na teh lokacijah, so upoštevani pri :doc:`vrednotenju "
"zalog <../product_management/inventory_valuation/using_inventory_valuation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Location`: where sold products are tracked; items here "
"are no longer in stock."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lokacija kupca`: kjer se spremljajo prodani izdelki; izdelki "
"tukaj niso več na zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inventory Loss`: counterpart location to consume missing items or "
"create stock, accounting for discrepancies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izguba zaloge`: protilokacija za porabo manjkajočih artiklov ali "
"ustvarjanje zaloge, ki upošteva neskladja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:75
msgid ""
"In Odoo, examples of inventory loss locations are *Inventory Adjustment*, "
"used to account for discrepancies during an inventory count, and *Scrap*, "
"which is where damaged goods are sent to account for inventory losses."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo so primeri lokacij za izgubo zalog *Inventory Adjustment*, ki se "
"uporablja za obračunavanje neskladij med štetjem zalog, in *Scrap*, kamor se "
"pošiljajo poškodovano blago za obračunavanje izgub zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:80
msgid ""
"`Virtual Locations/Inventory Adjustment` is a location with "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory Loss` type. The database shows `65` units in `WH/"
"Stock`, but an inventory check reveals `60`. To correct the quantity, five "
"units are moved from `WH/Stock` to `Virtual Locations/Inventory Adjustment`."
msgstr ""
"`Virtual Locations/Inventory Adjustment` je lokacija z vrsto "
":guilabel:`Izguba zalog`. Zbirka podatkov prikazuje `65` enot v `WH/Stock`, "
"vendar inventura razkrije `60`. Za popravek količine se pet enot premakne iz "
"`WH/Stock` v `Virtual Locations/Inventory Adjustment`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:0
msgid "Product ends up in Virtual Locations/Inventory Adjustment."
msgstr "Izdelek konča v Virtual Locations/Inventory Adjustment."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Production`: where raw materials are consumed, "
"and :doc:`manufactured products <../../manufacturing>` are created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Proizvodnja`: kjer se porabljajo surovine in :doc:`ustvarjajo "
"proizvedeni izdelki <../../manufacturing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Transit Location`: used for inter-company or inter-warehouse "
"operations to track products shipped between different addresses, such "
"as :ref:`Physical Locations/Inter-warehouse transit <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/interwarehouse-transit>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tranzitna lokacija`: uporablja se za medpodjetniške ali "
"medskladiščne operacije za sledenje izdelkov, poslanih med različnimi "
"naslovi, kot je :ref:`Physical Locations/Inter-warehouse transit <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/interwarehouse-transit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:None
msgid "List of locations in Odoo."
msgstr "Seznam lokacij v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:103
msgid "In Odoo, location types are color-coded:"
msgstr "V Odoo so vrste lokacij označene z barvami:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:102
msgid "**Red**: internal locations"
msgstr "**Rdeča**: notranje lokacije"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:103
msgid "**Blue**: view locations"
msgstr "**Modra**: lokacije pogleda"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:104
msgid ""
"**Black**: external locations (including inventory loss, vendor, and "
"customer locations)."
msgstr ""
"**Črna**: zunanje lokacije (vključno z izgubo zalog, lokacijami dobaviteljev "
"in kupcev)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:107
msgid "View locations in Odoo"
msgstr "Ogled lokacij v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:109
msgid ""
"Odoo databases include preconfigured view locations to organize the "
"hierarchy of locations. These provide helpful context, and distinguish "
"between internal and external locations."
msgstr ""
"Baze podatkov Odoo vključujejo vnaprej konfigurirane lokacije pogleda za "
"organizacijo hierarhije lokacij. Te zagotavljajo koristen kontekst in "
"razlikujejo med notranjimi in zunanjimi lokacijami."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:112
msgid ""
"*Physical locations* group internal locations—such as secondary warehouses "
"and subcontractor sites. Because :doc:`inventory valuation <../"
"product_management/inventory_valuation/inventory_valuation_config>` changes "
"only when goods move from internal to external locations, Odoo uses physical "
"locations to track stock that is off-site or in transit without affecting "
"valuation."
msgstr ""
"Fizične lokacije združujejo notranje lokacije, kot so sekundarna skladišča "
"in lokacije podizvajalcev. Ker se :doc:`vrednotenje zalog <../"
"product_management/inventory_valuation/inventory_valuation_config>` spremeni "
"le, ko se blago premakne iz notranjih na zunanje lokacije, Odoo uporablja "
"fizične lokacije za sledenje zalog, ki so zunaj lokacije ali v tranzitu, ne "
"da bi to vplivalo na vrednotenje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:121
msgid ""
"When moving products in warehouses `WH` and `WH2`, the items are not in "
"either warehouse, but still belong to the company. While in transit, they "
"are placed in the `Inter-warehouse transit` location, a :guilabel:`Transit "
"Location` type."
msgstr ""
"Pri premikanju izdelkov v skladiščih `WH` in `WH2` izdelki niso v nobenem "
"skladišču, vendar še vedno pripadajo podjetju. Med tranzitom so nameščeni na "
"lokaciji `Inter-warehouse transit`, ki je vrste :guilabel:`Tranzitna "
"lokacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:125
msgid ""
"This location is under the view location, `Physical Locations`, indicating "
"that `Inter-warehouse transit` is outside of a warehouse, but still part of "
"the company. Doing so does not affect the inventory valuation of the "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Ta lokacija je pod lokacijo pogleda `Physical Locations`, kar kaže, da je "
"`Inter-warehouse transit` zunaj skladišča, vendar še vedno del podjetja. To "
"ne vpliva na vrednotenje zalog izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:129
msgid ""
"*Partner locations* group customer and vendor locations (external locations) "
"together. Transfers to these locations affect inventory valuation."
msgstr ""
"*Partnerske lokacije* združujejo lokacije kupcev in dobaviteljev (zunanje "
"lokacije). Prenosi na te lokacije vplivajo na vrednotenje zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management.rst:131
msgid ""
"*Virtual locations* are locations that do **not** exist physically, but it "
"is where items that are not in inventory can be placed. These can be items "
"that are no longer in inventory due to loss, or other factors."
msgstr ""
"*Virtualne lokacije* so lokacije, ki fizično **ne** obstajajo, vendar so "
"mesto, kamor je mogoče postaviti artikle, ki niso na zalogi. To so lahko "
"artikli, ki zaradi izgube ali drugih dejavnikov niso več na zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:3
msgid "Inventory adjustments"
msgstr "Prilagoditve zalog"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:5
msgid ""
"In any warehouse management system, the recorded inventory counts in the "
"database might not always match the actual inventory counts in the "
"warehouse. The discrepancy between the two counts can be due to damages, "
"human errors, theft, or other factors. As such, inventory adjustments must "
"be made to reconcile the differences, and ensure that the recorded counts in "
"the database match the actual counts in the warehouse."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:14
msgid "Inventory Adjustments page"
msgstr "Stran Prilagoditve zalog"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:16
msgid ""
"To view the *Inventory Adjustments* page, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Physical Inventory`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid "In stock products listed on the Inventory adjustments page."
msgstr "Izdelki na zalogi, navedeni na strani Prilagoditve zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:22
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory Adjustments` table, all products that are "
"currently in stock are listed, with each product line containing the "
"following information:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:25
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Location`: the specific location in the warehouse where a product "
"is stored. This field needs to be enabled my going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings` and ticking "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` checkbox."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: the product whose quantity is listed on the inventory "
"adjustment line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izdelek`: izdelek, katerega količina je navedena v vrstici "
"prilagoditve zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number`: the tracking identifier assigned to the "
"specific product listed. It can contain letters, numbers, or a combination "
"of both."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lot/Serijska številka`: sledilni identifikator, dodeljen "
"določenemu navedenemu izdelku. Lahko vsebuje črke, številke ali kombinacijo "
"obojega."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`UoM`: the *unit of measure* in which the product is measured. "
"Unless otherwise specified (i.e., in :guilabel:`Pounds` "
"or :guilabel:`Ounces`), the default :abbr:`UoM (Unit of Measure)` "
"is :guilabel:`Units`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Counted Quantity`: the real quantity counted during an inventory "
"count. This field is left blank by default but can be changed, depending on "
"if it matches the :guilabel:`On Hand Quantity` or not."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prešteta količina`: dejanska količina, prešteta med popisom "
"zalog. To polje je privzeto prazno, vendar ga je mogoče spremeniti glede na "
"to, ali se ujema s :guilabel:`Količino na zalogi` ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Difference`: the difference between the :guilabel:`On Hand "
"Quantity` and :guilabel:`Counted Quantity`, once an inventory adjustment is "
"made. The difference is automatically calculated after every inventory "
"adjustment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Razlika`: razlika med :guilabel:`Količino na zalogi` in "
":guilabel:`Prešteto količino`, ko je opravljena prilagoditev zaloge. Razlika "
"se samodejno izračuna po vsaki prilagoditev zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:42
msgid ""
"If a specific product has a quantity of more than `1.00` in stock, and more "
"than one serial number (or lot number) is assigned, each uniquely-identified "
"product is displayed on its own product line with its own lot/serial number, "
"under the :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:46
msgid ""
"The fields below are optional and can be made visible by clicking "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings)` icon in the top right "
"of the :guilabel:`Inventory Adjustments` page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inventory Frequency (Days)`: the frequency, in days, for "
"inventory counts. The default value of this field is set to `0`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Favorite`: adds a clickable star icon next to each product. "
"Adding a favorite will bring the line item to the top of the dashboard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:53
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Category`: the category assigned internally to a specific "
"product. Unless otherwise specified (i.e., as :guilabel:`Consumable` "
"or :guilabel:`Rental`), the default *Product Category* is set "
"to :guilabel:`All`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expiration Date`: the date a product will expire, if it is a "
"perishable good. Only products that are tracked using lots and serial "
"numbers can be assigned expiration information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Last Count Date`: the date on which the last inventory count "
"occurred."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Available Quantity`: the quantity of a specific product that is "
"currently available, based on any outstanding/uncompleted sales orders, "
"purchase orders, or manufacturing orders that might change the available "
"quantity once fulfilled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:62
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Hand Quantity`: the quantity of the product currently recorded "
"in the database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Količina na zalogi`: količina izdelka, ki je trenutno zabeležena "
"v podatkovni bazi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounting Date`: the date on which the adjustments will be "
"accounted for in the Odoo **Accounting** app."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Scheduled Date`: the date at which a count should be made. If not "
"otherwise specified, this date defaults to the 31st of December of the "
"current year."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`User`: the person assigned to the count in the database. This can "
"either be the person physically counting the inventory, or applying the "
"count in the database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabnik`: oseba, dodeljena štetju v bazi podatkov. To je lahko "
"oseba, ki fizično šteje zalogo, ali oseba, ki vnese štetje v bazo podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:69
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: the company whose database these inventory adjustments "
"are being made on. The company is listed in the top-right corner of the "
"database, next to the user currently logged in."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:73
msgid ""
"Some columns are hidden by default. To reveal these columns, click "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings)` icon to the far right "
"of the form's top row, and select any desired column to reveal by clicking "
"the checkbox next to that option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:78
msgid ":doc:`Product type <../../product_management/configure/type>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:79
msgid ""
":doc:`Tracking with lots, serial numbers, and expiration dates <../../"
"product_management/product_tracking>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:83
msgid "Create an inventory adjustment"
msgstr "Ustvari inventurno prilagoditev"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:85
msgid ""
"To create a new inventory adjustment from the :ref:`Inventory Adjustments "
"<inventory/inventory-adjustments-page>` page, click :guilabel:`New`. Doing "
"so creates a new, blank inventory adjustment line at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:89
msgid ""
"On this blank inventory adjustment line, define the :guilabel:`Location` "
"where the product is stored. This is necessary to ensure the accuracy of the "
"inventory adjustment, as the same product can be stored in multiple "
"locations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:93
msgid ""
"Next, click the drop-down menu under the :guilabel:`Product` column, and "
"select a product. If the selected product is tracked using either lots or "
"serial numbers, the desired lot or serial number can also be chosen from the "
"drop-down menu under the :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:97
msgid ""
"Next, set the value in the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` column to the "
"quantity counted for that product during the inventory adjustment process."
msgstr ""
"Nato nastavite vrednost v stolpcu :guilabel:`Prešteta količina` na količino, "
"ki je bila prešteta za ta izdelek med postopkom prilagoditve zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:100
msgid ""
"To the right of the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` column, "
"the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` and :guilabel:`User` can also be changed via "
"their respective drop-down menus. Changing the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` "
"changes the date that the inventory adjustment should be processed on, and "
"selecting a responsible :guilabel:`User` assigns a user to the specific "
"inventory adjustment (for traceability purposes)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once all changes have been made to the new inventory adjustment line, click "
"away from the line. Doing so saves the adjustment, and moves the line to the "
"top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse spremembe opravljene v novi vrstici prilagoditve zaloge, kliknite "
"stran od vrstice. S tem se prilagoditev shrani in vrstica se premakne na vrh "
"strani."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:109
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` is greater than the :guilabel:`On Hand "
"Quantity`, the value in the :guilabel:`Difference` column is **green**. If "
"the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` is less than the :guilabel:`On Hand "
"Quantity`, the value in the :guilabel:`Difference` column is **red**. If the "
"quantities match, and haven't been changed at all, no value appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Difference` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid "Difference column on inventory adjustments page."
msgstr "Stolpec Razlika na strani prilagoditev zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:118
msgid ""
"At this stage, the count (:dfn:`inventory adjustment`) is recorded, but not "
"yet applied. This means that the quantity on hand before the adjustment has "
"not yet been updated to match the new, real counted quantity."
msgstr ""
"V tej fazi je štetje (:dfn:`prilagoditev zaloge`) zabeleženo, vendar še ni "
"uporabljeno. To pomeni, da količina na zalogi pred prilagoditvijo še ni bila "
"posodobljena, da bi se ujemala z novo, dejansko prešteto količino."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:122
msgid ""
"There are two ways to apply the new inventory adjustment. The first way is "
"to click the :icon:`fa-save` :guilabel:`Apply` button on the line at the far "
"right of the page. The second way is to click the checkbox on the far left "
"of the line. Doing so reveals new button options at the top of the page, one "
"of which is an :guilabel:`Apply` button. Clicking this button instead causes "
"an :guilabel:`Inventory Adjustment` pop-up window to appear."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid ""
"Apply all option applies the inventory adjustment once a reason is specified."
msgstr "Možnost Uporabi vse uporabi prilagoditev zaloge, ko je naveden razlog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:131
msgid ""
"From this pop-up menu, a reference or reason can be assigned to the "
"inventory adjustment. By default, the :guilabel:`Inventory Reason` field is "
"pre-populated with the date the adjustment is being made on, but can be "
"changed to reflect whatever reference or reason is desired."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:135
msgid "Once ready, click :guilabel:`Apply` to apply the inventory adjustment."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste pripravljeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`, da uporabite prilagoditev "
"zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:138
msgid ""
"Applying an inventory adjustment simultaneously creates a :doc:`stock move "
"line (SML) <../reporting/moves_history>` in the *Moves History* report for "
"traceability."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba prilagoditve zaloge hkrati ustvari :doc:`vrstico skladiščnega "
"prenosa (SML) <../reporting/moves_history>` v poročilu *Zgodovina premikov* "
"za sledljivost."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:142
msgid ""
"Sometimes products end up in unexpected or incorrect locations. To quickly "
"move a product to a different storage location, check the box next to the "
"product, and click the :guilabel:`Relocate` button at the top of "
"the :ref:`Inventory Adjustments <inventory/inventory-adjustments-page>` page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:148
msgid "Count products"
msgstr "Preštej izdelke"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:150
msgid ""
"Counting products (or stock-taking) is a recurring warehouse process to "
"verify the physical quantity of items against internal inventory records. "
"The values recorded on file versus what is actually counted in real life "
"sometimes do not match, so inventory adjustments can be made on the "
"*Inventory Adjustments* dashboard."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:155
msgid ""
"Once a count is complete, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations "
"--> Physical Inventory` to verify and update product :guilabel:`Count "
"Quantities`, as it is necessary to do so."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:159
msgid ""
"To print a PDF of a count sheet, first select the desired product "
"checkboxes, and then click the :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print` button "
"that appears at the top of the dashboard. Then, select the :guilabel:`Count "
"sheet` option in the sub-menu, which will download a PDF detailing the "
"selected products."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:164
msgid ""
"On each product line, identify whether the value in the :guilabel:`On Hand "
"Quantity` column recorded in the database matches the newly-counted value. "
"If the recorded value and the counted value do match, select the product "
"using the checkbox, click the :guilabel:`Actions` button, "
"then :guilabel:`Set to quantity on hand`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:169
msgid ""
"Doing so copies the value from the :guilabel:`On Hand Quantity` column over "
"to the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` column, and sets the value of "
"the :guilabel:`Difference` column to `0.00`. Subsequently, once applied, an "
"inventory move with `0.00` :guilabel:`Quantity Done` is recorded in the "
"product's inventory adjustment history."
msgstr ""
"S tem se vrednost iz stolpca :guilabel:`Količina na zalogi` prekopira v "
"stolpec :guilabel:`Prešteta količina` in nastavi vrednost stolpca "
":guilabel:`Razlika` na `0.00`. Posledično se po uporabi v zgodovini "
"prilagoditev zaloge izdelka zabeleži skladiščni prenos z `0.00` "
":guilabel:`Opravljeno količine`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid "Zero count inventory adjustment move."
msgstr "Premik inventurne prilagoditve z ničelnim štetjem."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:177
msgid ""
"If the newly-counted value for a given product does **not** match the value "
"in the :guilabel:`On Hand Quantity` recorded in the database, instead of "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Set` button, record the real value in the field in "
"the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:181
msgid ""
"To do so, click the field in the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` column on the "
"specific inventory adjustment line for the product whose count is being "
"changed. This automatically assigns a :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` of `0.00`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite to storiti, kliknite polje v stolpcu :guilabel:`Prešteta količina` "
"v vrstici prilagoditve zaloge za izdelek, katerega štetje se spreminja. To "
"samodejno dodeli :guilabel:`Prešteto količino` `0.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:185
msgid ""
"To change this value, type in a new value that matches the real, newly-"
"counted value. Then, click away from the line. Doing so saves the "
"adjustment, and automatically adjusts the value in "
"the :guilabel:`Difference` column."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti to vrednost, vnesite novo vrednost, ki ustreza "
"dejanski, na novo prešteti vrednosti. Nato kliknite stran od vrstice. S tem "
"shranite prilagoditev in samodejno prilagodite vrednost v "
"stolpcu :guilabel:`Razlika`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:189
msgid ""
"Subsequently, once applied, a move with the difference between "
"the :guilabel:`On Hand Quantity` and the :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` is "
"recorded in the product's inventory adjustment history."
msgstr ""
"Posledično se po uporabi v zgodovini prilagoditev zaloge izdelka zabeleži "
"prenos z razliko med :guilabel:`Količino na zalogi` in :guilabel:`Prešteto "
"količino`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid ""
"Inventory Adjustments History dashboard detailing a list of prior product "
"moves."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorna plošča zgodovine inventurnih prilagoditev s seznamom prejšnjih "
"premikov izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:195
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Actions` menu appears when one or more products' checkboxes "
"are selected. The :guilabel:`Actions` menu includes the option "
"to :guilabel:`Set to quantity on hand`, which sets the selected "
"products' :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` to the :guilabel:`On Hand Quantity`, "
"and :guilabel:`Set to 0`, which sets the selected "
"products' :guilabel:`Counted Quantity` to zero."
msgstr ""
"Meni :guilabel:`Dejanja` se prikaže, ko so izbrana potrditvena polja enega "
"ali več izdelkov. Meni :guilabel:`Dejanja` vključuje možnost "
":guilabel:`Nastavi na količino na zalogi`, ki nastavi :guilabel:`Prešteto "
"količino` izbranih izdelkov na :guilabel:`Količino na zalogi`, in "
":guilabel:`Nastavi na 0`, ki nastavi :guilabel:`Prešteto količino` izbranih "
"izdelkov na nič."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid "Inventory Adjustments Actions menu."
msgstr "Dejanja menija za popravke zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:204
msgid ""
"Sometimes a count occurs, but cannot be applied in the database right away. "
"In the time between the actual count and applying the inventory adjustment, "
"product moves can occur. In that case, the on-hand quantity in the database "
"can change and no longer be consistent with the counted quantity. As an "
"extra precaution, Odoo asks for confirmation before applying the inventory "
"adjustment."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se štetje izvede, vendar ga ni mogoče takoj uporabiti v bazi "
"podatkov. V času med dejanskim štetjem in uporabo prilagoditve zaloge se "
"lahko zgodijo premiki izdelkov. V tem primeru se lahko razpoložljiva "
"količina v bazi podatkov spremeni in ni več skladna s prešteto količino. Kot "
"dodatni ukrep Odoo zahteva potrditev pred uporabo prilagoditve zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:211
msgid "Plan inventory counts"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:213
msgid ""
"To plan inventory counts, such as a full count of everything currently in "
"stock, first navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> "
"Physical Inventory`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:216
msgid ""
"Then, select the desired products to be counted by clicking the checkbox on "
"the far left of each product line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:220
msgid ""
"To request a count of **all** products currently in stock, click the "
"checkbox at the very top of the table, in the header row next to "
"the :guilabel:`Location` label. This selects **all** product lines."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:224
msgid ""
"Once all desired products have been selected, click the :guilabel:`Request a "
"Count` button at the top of the page. Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Request "
"a Count` pop-up window, where the following information can be filled:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi želeni izdelki izbrani, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Zahtevaj štetje` "
"na vrhu strani. S tem se odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Zahtevaj štetje`, "
"kjer lahko izpolnite naslednje podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:228
msgid ":guilabel:`Inventory Date`: the planned date of the count."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum zaloge`: načrtovani datum štetja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:229
msgid ":guilabel:`User`: the user responsible for the count."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabnik`: uporabnik, odgovoren za štetje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:230
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounting Date`: the date at which the inventory adjustment will "
"be accounted."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Računovodski datum`: datum, na katerega bo prilagoditev zaloge "
"knjižena."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:231
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Count`: to leave the on-hand quantity of each product line blank, "
"select :guilabel:`Leave Empty`. To pre-fill the on-hand quantity of each "
"product line with the current value recorded in the database, "
"select :guilabel:`Set Current Value`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Štetje`: če želite pustiti količino na zalogi za vsako vrstico "
"izdelka prazno, izberite :guilabel:`Pusti prazno`. Če želite vnaprej "
"izpolniti količino na zalogi za vsako vrstico izdelka s trenutno vrednostjo, "
"zabeleženo v podatkovni bazi, izberite :guilabel:`Nastavi trenutno vrednost`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:235
msgid "Finally, once ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to request the count."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje, ko ste pripravljeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da zahtevate "
"štetje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:None
msgid "Request a count popup on inventory adjustments page."
msgstr "Pojavno okno Zahtevaj štetje na strani prilagoditev zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:241
msgid ""
"In the Odoo **Barcode** app, users can only view inventory counts that are "
"assigned to **them**, and are scheduled for **today** or **earlier**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products.rst:245
msgid ":doc:`cycle_counts`"
msgstr ":doc:`cycle_counts`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:3
msgid "Cycle counts"
msgstr "Ciklično štetje"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:5
msgid ""
"For most companies, warehouse stock only needs to be counted once a year. "
"This is why, by default, the scheduled date for the next inventory count is "
"set for the 31st of December of the current year."
msgstr ""
"Pri večini podjetij je treba zalogo v skladišču prešteti le enkrat letno. "
"Zato je privzeto načrtovani datum naslednjega štetja zaloge nastavljen na "
"31. december tekočega leta."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:8
msgid ""
"However, for some businesses, maintaining an accurate inventory count is "
"crucial. These companies use *cycle counts* to keep critical stock levels "
"accurate. Cycle counting is a method by which companies count their "
"inventory more often in certain *locations* to ensure that their physical "
"inventory counts match their inventory records."
msgstr ""
"Vendar je za nekatera podjetja vzdrževanje natančnega štetja zaloge "
"ključnega pomena. Ta podjetja uporabljajo *ciklična štetja*, da ohranjajo "
"natančne ravni kritične zaloge. Ciklično štetje je metoda, s katero podjetja "
"pogosteje štejejo svojo zalogo na določenih *lokacijah*, da zagotovijo "
"ujemanje dejanskih količin zaloge z evidencami o zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:16
msgid ""
"In Odoo, cycle counts are performed by location. Therefore, the *Storage "
"Locations* feature needs to be enabled before performing a cycle count."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo se ciklično štetje izvaja po lokaciji. Zato je treba pred izvajanjem "
"cikličnega štetja omogočiti funkcijo *Lokacije za shranjevanje*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:19
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll down to the *Warehouse* section. "
"Then, select the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Storage Locations` and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:None
msgid "Enabled Storage Locations setting in inventory settings."
msgstr "Omogočena nastavitev Lokacije za shranjevanje v nastavitvah zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:27
msgid "Counting inventory at a set frequency"
msgstr "Štetje zaloge s določeno frekvenco"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:29
msgid ""
"After the *Storage Locations* feature is enabled and locations are created "
"in the warehouse, the inventory count frequency can be changed for specific "
"locations, and counts can be conducted on those locations."
msgstr ""
"Ko je funkcija *Lokacije skladiščenja* omogočena in so lokacije ustvarjene v "
"skladišču, je mogoče spremeniti pogostost štetja zaloge za določene lokacije "
"ter izvajati štetja na teh lokacijah."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:34
msgid "Setting a cycle count frequency"
msgstr "Nastavitev frekvence cikličnega štetja"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:36
msgid ""
"To view and edit locations, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Locations`. This opens a *Locations* page listing every "
"location currently created in the warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled in urejanje lokacij odprite :menuselection:`Zaloga --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Lokacije`. To odpre stran *Lokacije*, ki navaja vse "
"trenutno ustvarjene lokacije v skladišču."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:39
msgid "From this page, click a location to open its form."
msgstr "Na tej strani kliknite lokacijo, da odprete njen obrazec."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:41
msgid ""
"Under the *Cyclic Counting* section, locate the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Frequency (Days)` field, which is set to `0` by default (if this location "
"has not been edited previously). In this field, change the value to any "
"number of days desired for the frequency of counts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:None
msgid "Location frequency setting on location."
msgstr "Nastavitev pogostosti lokacije na lokaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:49
msgid ""
"A location that needs an inventory count every 30 days should have "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory Frequency (Days)` value set to `30`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:52
msgid ""
"Now, to ensure the scheduled cycle count appears as expected, :ref:`perform "
"the first cycle count <inventory/warehouses_storage/cycle_count_perform>`. "
"After inventory adjustments have been applied to the products in this "
"location, the next scheduled count date is automatically set based on the "
"value entered in the :guilabel:`Inventory Frequency (Days)` field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:60
msgid "Performing a cycle count"
msgstr "Izvajanje cikličnega štetja"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:62
msgid ""
"To perform a cycle count for a specific location in the warehouse, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Physical Inventory`. "
"This opens an *Inventory Adjustments* page that lists all products currently "
"in stock, with each product on its own line."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti ciklično štetje za določeno lokacijo v skladišču, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Operacije --> Fizični popis`. Odprla se bo "
"stran *Prilagoditve zaloge*, ki navaja vse izdelke, ki so trenutno na "
"zalogi, pri čemer je vsak izdelek na svoji vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:66
msgid ""
"From this page, the :guilabel:`Filters` and :guilabel:`Group By` options "
"(accessible by clicking the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` "
"icon to the right of the :guilabel:`Search` bar) can be used to select "
"specific locations and perform inventory counts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:70
msgid ""
"To select a specific location and view all products within that location, "
"click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` icon to the right "
"of the :guilabel:`Search` bar. Then, in the :guilabel:`Group By` column, "
"select :guilabel:`Location`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:None
msgid "Filters and Group By menu on Inventory Adjustments page."
msgstr "Meni Filtri in Združi po na strani Prilagoditve zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:77
msgid ""
"All products are sorted into their storage locations on the *Inventory "
"Adjustments* page, and a cycle count can be performed for all products in "
"that location."
msgstr ""
"Vsi izdelki so razvrščeni v svoje lokacije skladiščenja na strani "
"*Prilagoditve zaloge* in za vse izdelke na tej lokaciji je mogoče izvesti "
"ciklično štetje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:81
msgid ""
"In large warehouses with multiple locations and a high volume of products, "
"it might be easier to search for the desired location. To do this, from the "
"*Inventory Adjustments* page, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` icon to the right of the :guilabel:`Search` "
"bar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:85
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Filters` column, click :guilabel:`Add Custom Filter` "
"to open an *Add Custom Filter* pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Nato v stolpcu :guilabel:`Filtri` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj filter po meri`, "
"da odprete pojavno okno *Dodaj filter po meri*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:88
msgid ""
"In the first field, click the value and select :guilabel:`Location` from the "
"list of options. Select :guilabel:`contains` in the second field. In the "
"third field, type in the name of the location being searched for."
msgstr ""
"V prvem polju kliknite vrednost in s seznama možnosti "
"izberite :guilabel:`Lokacija`. V drugem polju izberite :guilabel:`vsebuje`. "
"V tretje polje vnesite ime lokacije, ki jo iščete."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:92
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Add` for that location to appear on the page."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`, da se ta lokacija prikaže na strani."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:0
msgid "Add Custom Filter pop-up window with location values entered."
msgstr "Pojavno okno Dodaj filter po meri z vnešenimi vrednostmi lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:98
msgid ""
"When performing counts in the *Barcode* app, inventory adjustments are "
"grouped by location by default."
msgstr ""
"Pri izvajanju štetij v aplikaciji *Črtna koda* so popisi zaloge privzeto "
"združeni po lokaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:102
msgid "Change full inventory count date"
msgstr "Sprememba datuma celotnega popisa zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:104
msgid ""
"While cycle counts are typically performed on the location, companies should "
"conduct a full inventory count once per year. In addition to keeping stock "
"counts accurate, full inventory counts ensure that accounting earnings and "
"costs are recorded accurately. The scheduled date for full inventory counts "
"of all in-stock products in the warehouse can be manually changed to push it "
"up earlier than the listed date."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:110
msgid ""
"To modify the default scheduled date, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`. Then, in the *Operations* section, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Annual Inventory Day and Month` setting, which includes drop-"
"down fields set to `31` :guilabel:`December` by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:None
msgid "Frequency field in inventory app settings."
msgstr "Polje Pogostost v nastavitvah aplikacije Zaloga."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:117
msgid ""
"To change the day, click the `31` and select a day within the range `1-31`, "
"depending on the desired month of the year."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti dan, kliknite `31` in izberite dan v obsegu `1-31`, "
"odvisno od želenega meseca v letu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:120
msgid ""
"Then, to change the month, click :guilabel:`December` to reveal the drop-"
"down menu and select the desired month."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:123
msgid "After all necessary changes have been made, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Ko so vse potrebne spremembe opravljene, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:126
msgid ":doc:`count_products`"
msgstr ":doc:`count_products`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/cycle_counts.rst:127
msgid ":doc:`use_locations`"
msgstr ":doc:`use_locations`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:3
msgid "Scrap inventory"
msgstr "Odpis zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:8
msgid ""
"Sometimes, products in a company's warehouse stock might be found to be "
"damaged or defective, past the point of being reparable. If it is not "
"possible to repair the product, or return the product to a vendor, it can be "
"scrapped."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se lahko ugotovi, da so izdelki v zalogah skladišča podjetja "
"poškodovani ali pomanjkljivi, zunaj možnosti popravila. Če izdelka ni mogoče "
"popraviti ali vrniti dobavitelju, ga je mogoče odpisati."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:12
msgid ""
"Odoo *Inventory* allows users to scrap inventory, designating goods or "
"materials that are no longer usable or sellable for disposal (or recycling)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Inventory* uporabnikom omogoča odpis zaloge, s čimer določijo blago "
"ali materiale, ki niso več uporabni ali prodajni, za odstranitev (ali "
"recikliranje)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:15
msgid ""
"Scrapping inventory in a database helps stock counts remain accurate, by "
"removing scrapped products from physical inventory, and placing it in a "
"virtual scrap location (*Virtual Locations/Scrap*)."
msgstr ""
"Izločanje zaloge v podatkovni bazi pomaga ohranjati natančne štetje zalog, "
"tako da odstrani izločene izdelke iz fizične zaloge in jih premesti v "
"virtualno lokacijo izločanja (*Virtualne lokacije/Izločanje*)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:19
msgid ""
"*Virtual locations* in Odoo are **not** real, physical spaces in a "
"warehouse. Rather, they are designated locations in a database that provide "
"tracking of items that shouldn't be counted in a physical inventory."
msgstr ""
"*Virtualne lokacije* v Odoo **niso** resnični, fizični prostori v skladišču. "
"Gre za določene lokacije v zbirki podatkov, ki omogočajo sledenje elementom, "
"ki se ne smejo šteti v fizični inventuri."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:23
msgid ""
"For more information about virtual locations, see the documentation about "
"the different types of :ref:`location types <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"location-type>`."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o virtualnih lokacijah glejte dokumentacijo o različnih "
"vrstah :ref:`vrst lokacij <inventory/warehouses_storage/location-type>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:27
msgid "Scrap from stock"
msgstr "Odpis iz zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:29
msgid ""
"To create a new scrap order (SP) for an in-stock product, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Scrap`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. This opens a new |SP| form."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega naloga za odpis (SP) za izdelek na zalogi se pomaknite "
"na :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Scrap` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`New`. To odpre nov obrazec |SP|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:32
msgid ""
"Click the drop-down menu in the :guilabel:`Product` field, and select the "
"product that should be scrapped from inventory. In the :guilabel:`Quantity` "
"field, change the value to the quantity of the product that should be "
"scrapped (by default, this value is set to `1.00`)."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite spustni meni v polju :guilabel:`Product` in izberite izdelek, ki "
"naj bo odpisan iz zaloge. V polju :guilabel:`Quantity` spremenite vrednost "
"na količino izdelka, ki naj bo odpisan (privzeto je ta vrednost nastavljena "
"na `1.00`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:None
msgid "Filled out new scrap order form with product details."
msgstr "Izpolnjen nov obrazec za odpis z podrobnostmi o izdelku."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:40
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Source Location` defaults to the location where the product "
"is currently stored. The :guilabel:`Scrap Location` defaults to the "
"designated scrap location (:guilabel:`Virtual Locations/Scrap`). Either of "
"these locations can be changed by selecting a different location from their "
"respective drop-down menus."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izvorna lokacija` je privzeto nastavljena na lokacijo, kjer je "
"izdelek trenutno shranjen. :guilabel:`Lokacija odpadkov` je privzeto "
"nastavljena na določeno lokacijo za odpadke (:guilabel:`Navidezne lokacije/"
"Odpadki`). Obe lokaciji lahko spremenite tako, da iz ustreznih spustnih "
"menijev izberete drugo lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:45
msgid ""
"If the scrapping is tied to a specific existing operation, specify the "
"operation in the :guilabel:`Source Document` field."
msgstr ""
"Če je odpis vezan na določeno obstoječo operacijo, navedite operacijo v "
"polju :guilabel:`Source Document`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:48
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company` field displays the company whose warehouse this "
"product belongs to. If a replenishment rule is set up for the product being "
"scrapped, and if the product should be replenished, tick the checkbox "
"for :guilabel:`Replenish Quantities`."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Podjetje` prikazuje podjetje, katerega skladišču ta izdelek "
"pripada. Če je za izdelek, ki se odpisuje, nastavljena pravila oskrbe in če "
"je treba izdelek oskrbeti, označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Oskrbi "
"količine`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:52
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the new |SP|. Once "
"validated, a :guilabel:`Product Moves` smart button appears at the top of "
"the form. Click the smart button to view the details of the scrap operation."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste pripravljeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da dokončate nov |SP|. Ko "
"je potrjeno, se na vrhu obrazca prikaže pametno gumb :guilabel:`Premiki "
"izdelkov`. Kliknite pametni gumb, da si ogledate podrobnosti operacije "
"odpisa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:None
msgid "Product Moves smart button on new scrap order form."
msgstr "Pametni gumb Premiki izdelkov na obrazcu novega naloga za odpadke."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:61
msgid ""
"To view the all-time total quantities of scrapped items, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. Click "
"the :guilabel:`x (remove)` button on the :guilabel:`Internal` filter in "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` bar, to display virtual locations."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati skupne količine odpisanih postavk za vse čase, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Lokacije`. "
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`x (odstrani)` na filtru :guilabel:`Interno` v "
"vrstici :guilabel:`Iskanje...`, da prikažete navidezne lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:65
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Virtual Locations/Scrap` location. From "
"the :guilabel:`Scrap` location's form, click the :guilabel:`Current Stock` "
"smart button, at the top of the form."
msgstr ""
"Izberite lokacijo :guilabel:`Navidezne lokacije/Odpadki`. Na obrazcu "
"lokacije :guilabel:`Odpadki` kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Trenutna "
"zaloga` na vrhu obrazca."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:68
msgid "A list of all scrapped products, and their quantities, is displayed."
msgstr "Prikazan je seznam vseh odpisanih izdelkov in njihovih količin."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:0
msgid "Current Stock list of all scrapped products in virtual scrap location."
msgstr ""
"Seznam Trenutna zaloga vseh odpisanih izdelkov v navidezni lokaciji odpadkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:75
msgid "Scrap from an existing operation"
msgstr "Odpis iz obstoječe operacije"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:77
msgid ""
"Scrap orders (SPs) can *also* be created from existing operations, such as "
"receipts, delivery orders, and internal transfers, before they are entered "
"into, or removed from, stock for an operation."
msgstr ""
"Naloge za odpis (SP) je mogoče ustvariti *tudi* iz obstoječih operacij, kot "
"so prejemi, dobavnice in notranji prenosi, preden so vneseni v zalogo ali "
"odstranjeni iz nje za operacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:81
msgid ""
"To scrap a product during an operation, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Inventory app`. From the :guilabel:`Inventory Overview`, "
"click the :guilabel:`# To Process` button on an operation's task card (i.e. "
"the :guilabel:`Receipts` task card)."
msgstr ""
"Za odpis izdelka med operacijo se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Inventory "
"app`. Iz :guilabel:`Inventory Overview` kliknite gumb :guilabel:`# To "
"Process` na kartici opravila operacije (npr. kartica "
"opravila :guilabel:`Receipts`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:None
msgid "# To Process button on Receipts task card on Inventory Overview page."
msgstr "Gumb # Za obdelavo na kartici opravila Prejemi na strani Pregled zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:89
msgid ""
"Then, select an operation to process from the resulting list of existing "
"orders. Doing so opens that operation's form."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite operacijo za obdelavo s seznama obstoječih nalogov. S tem se "
"odpre obrazec te operacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:92
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(cog)` icon, and "
"select :guilabel:`Scrap` from the resulting drop-down menu. This opens "
"a :guilabel:`Scrap Products` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)` in iz spustnega menija "
"izberite :guilabel:`Odpiši`. S tem se odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Odpiši "
"izdelke`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:None
msgid "Scrap Products pop-up window on operation form."
msgstr "Pojavno okno Scrap Products na obrazcu operacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:99
msgid ""
"From this pop-up window, click the drop-down menu in the :guilabel:`Product` "
"field, and select the products from the operation that should be scrapped. "
"Adjust the value in the :guilabel:`Quantity` field, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"V tem pojavnem oknu kliknite spustni meni v polju :guilabel:`Izdelek` in "
"izberite izdelke iz operacije, ki jih je treba odpisati. Po potrebi "
"prilagodite vrednost v polju :guilabel:`Količina`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Product` selected is tracked using a lot or serial number, "
"a :guilabel:`Lot/Serial` field appears. Specify the tracking number in that "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Product`, ki je izbran, sledljiv z uporabo serije ali "
"serijske številke, se prikaže polje :guilabel:`Lot/Serial`. V to polje "
"navedite številko sledenja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:106
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Source Location` and :guilabel:`Scrap Location` can be "
"changed, if needed. If a replenishment rule is set up for the product being "
"scrapped, and if the product should be replenished, tick the checkbox "
"for :guilabel:`Replenish Quantities`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izvorna lokacija` in :guilabel:`Lokacija odpadkov` se lahko po "
"potrebi spremenita. Če je za izdelek, ki se odpisuje, nastavljena pravila "
"oskrbe in če je treba izdelek oskrbeti, označite potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Oskrbi količine`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:110
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Scrap Products`. A :guilabel:`Scraps` smart "
"button appears at the top of the operation form. Click this smart button to "
"view the details of all scrap orders created from this specific operation."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste pripravljeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Odpiši izdelke`. Na vrhu obrazca "
"operacije se prikaže pametni gumb :guilabel:`Odpadki`. Kliknite ta pametni "
"gumb, da si ogledate podrobnosti vseh nalogov za odpadke, ustvarjenih iz te "
"specifične operacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/scrap_inventory.rst:None
msgid "Scraps smart button showing all scrap orders from operation."
msgstr "Pametni gumb Odpadki, ki prikazuje vse naloge za odpadke iz operacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *location* is a specific space within a warehouse. This can be a shelf, "
"room, aisle, etc."
msgstr ""
"*Lokacija* je določen prostor znotraj skladišča. To je lahko polica, soba, "
"hodnik itd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:12
msgid ""
"To create specific storage locations, enable the *Storage Locations* feature "
"by going to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"In the :guilabel:`Warehouses` section, tick the :guilabel:`Storage "
"Locations` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje specifičnih skladiščnih lokacij omogočite funkcijo "
"*Skladiščne lokacije* tako, da greste na :menuselection:`aplikacija Zaloga --"
"> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Skladišča` označite "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Skladiščne lokacije`. Nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:17
msgid ""
"Typically, the :guilabel:`Storage Locations` feature is used "
"with :doc:`Multi-Step Routes <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"use_routes>`, which controls how products move between locations."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija :guilabel:`Skladiščne lokacije` se običajno uporablja skupaj s "
"funkcijo :doc:`Večstopenjske poti <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"use_routes>`, ki nadzoruje, kako se izdelki premikajo med lokacijami."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:None
msgid "Show Storage Locations feature."
msgstr "Prikaz funkcije Skladiščne lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:26
msgid "Create new location"
msgstr "Ustvari novo lokacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:28
msgid ""
"After enabling *Storage Locations*, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Locations`."
msgstr ""
"Po omogočanju funkcije *Skladiščne lokacije* greste "
"na :menuselection:`aplikacija Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Lokacije`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:None
msgid "List of internal locations."
msgstr "Seznam notranjih lokacij."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:35
msgid ""
"On this page, click :guilabel:`New`. The new location form can then be "
"configured as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Obrazec nove lokacije lahko nato "
"konfigurirate na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:37
msgid ":guilabel:`Location Name`: recognizable name of the location."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime lokacije`: prepoznavno ime lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Parent Location`: the location within which the new location "
"exists. After the location is created, it is listed on "
"the :guilabel:`Locations` page using a *location hierarchy*, to describe how "
"a specific location fits within larger areas of the warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nadrejena lokacija`: lokacija, znotraj katere obstaja nova "
"lokacija. Po ustvarjanju lokacije je ta navedena na "
"strani :guilabel:`Lokacije` z uporabo *hierarhije lokacij*, da opiše, kako "
"se določena lokacija ujema z večjimi območji skladišča."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:43
msgid ""
"In `WH/Stock/Zone A/Refrigerator 1`, \"Refrigerator 1\" is the location "
"name, \"Zone A\" is the parent location, and everything before it is the "
"path showing where this spot is within the warehouse."
msgstr ""
"V `WH/Stock/Cona A/Hladilnik 1` je \"Hladilnik 1\" ime lokacije, \"Cona A\" "
"je nadrejena lokacija, vse pred tem pa je pot, ki prikazuje, kje se to mesto "
"nahaja v skladišču."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:48
msgid "Additional Information section"
msgstr "Razdelek Dodatne informacije"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:50
msgid ""
"In addition to the required fields above, configure the following location "
"fields to ensure the location serves its intended purpose in the database:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg zgoraj navedenih obveznih polj konfigurirajte naslednja polja "
"lokacije, da zagotovite, da lokacija služi svojemu predvidenemu namenu v "
"bazi podatkov:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:53
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Location Type`: from the drop-down menu, choose :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Location`, :guilabel:`View`, :guilabel:`Internal "
"Location`, :guilabel:`Customer Location`, :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Loss`, :guilabel:`Production`, or :guilabel:`Transit Location` to categorize "
"the location. For details on each location type, refer to the :ref:`Location "
"Types section <inventory/warehouses_storage/location-type>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta lokacije`: iz spustnega menija izberite :guilabel:`Lokacija "
"dobavitelja`, :guilabel:`Pogled`, :guilabel:`Interna lokacija`, "
":guilabel:`Lokacija stranke`, :guilabel:`Izguba zalog`, "
":guilabel:`Proizvodnja` ali :guilabel:`Tranzitna lokacija`, da "
"kategorizirate lokacijo. Za podrobnosti o posameznih vrstah lokacij glejte "
":ref:`razdelek Vrste lokacij <inventory/warehouses_storage/location-type>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Storage Category`: only available with the :doc:`Storage "
"Categories <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category>` "
"feature enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategorija skladiščenja`: na voljo samo, če je "
"funkcija :doc:`Kategorije skladiščenja <../../shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations/storage_category>` omogočena v :menuselection:`aplikacija "
"Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`Company`: the company the location belongs to."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Podjetje`: podjetje, kateremu lokacija pripada."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is a Scrap Location?`: tick this checkbox to allow for scrapped/"
"damaged goods to be stored in this location."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je lokacija odpadkov?`: označite to potrditveno polje, da "
"omogočite shranjevanje odpisanega/poškodovanega blaga na tej lokaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:64
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is a Return Location?`: tick this checkbox to allow products to "
"be returned to this location."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je lokacija vračil?`: označite to potrditveno polje, da omogočite "
"vračanje izdelkov na to lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Barcode`: used with the *Barcode* app, enter the barcode "
"to :ref:`identify actions <barcode/setup/location>` at this location when "
"scanned."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Črtna koda`: uporablja se z aplikacijo *Črtna koda*, vnesite "
"črtno kodo za :ref:`identifikacijo dejanj <barcode/setup/location>` na tej "
"lokaciji ob skeniranju."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Replenish Location`: used for :doc:`configuring routes <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes>`, tick this checkbox to set "
"the location as a destination for receiving products from *Buy*, "
"*Manufacture*, or other procurement routes, ensuring products are correctly "
"supplied to the warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oskrbi lokacijo`: uporablja se za :doc:`konfiguracijo poti <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes>`, označite to potrditveno "
"polje, da nastavite lokacijo kot cilj za prejemanje izdelkov iz poti "
"*Nakup*, *Proizvodnja* ali drugih poti oskrbe, s čimer zagotovite, da so "
"izdelki pravilno dobavljeni v skladišče."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:None
msgid "Additional Information section of new location creation form."
msgstr "Razdelek Dodatne informacije obrazca za ustvarjanje nove lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:77
msgid ""
"Configure the remaining fields in the :guilabel:`Additional Information` "
"section as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte preostala polja v razdelku :guilabel:`Dodatne informacije` na "
"naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: the company whose warehouse the location is inside of. "
"Leave this field blank if this location is shared between companies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podjetje`: podjetje, v katerem skladišču se lokacija nahaja. To "
"polje pustite prazno, če je lokacija skupna med podjetji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:85
msgid ":guilabel:`Barcode`: the barcode assigned to the location."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Črtna koda`: črtna koda, dodeljena lokaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Replenish Location`: tick this checkbox to get all quantities to "
"replenish at this location."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lokacija za dopolnjevanje`: označite to potrditveno polje, če "
"želite pridobiti vse količine za dopolnitev na tej lokaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:89
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Cyclic Counting` section, change the value in "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory Frequency (Days)` field from the default `0`, if "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Ciklično štetje` po potrebi spremenite vrednost v "
"polju :guilabel:`Pogostost inventure (dnevi)` iz privzete vrednosti `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:None
msgid "Cyclic Counting section of new location creation form."
msgstr "Razdelek Ciklično štetje obrazca za ustvarjanje nove lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:96
msgid ""
"When different than `0`, the inventory count dates for products stored at "
"this location are automatically set at the defined frequency."
msgstr ""
"Če je različno od `0`, se datumi inventurnega štetja za izdelke, shranjene "
"na tej lokaciji, samodejno nastavijo z določeno frekvenco."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:99
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Logistics` section, in the :guilabel:`Removal Strategy` "
"field, click the drop-down menu and select the :doc:`removal strategy <../../"
"shipping_receiving/removal_strategies>` for how items should be removed from "
"this location."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Logistika` v polju :guilabel:`Strategija odvzema` "
"kliknite spustni meni in izberite :doc:`strategijo odvzema <../../"
"shipping_receiving/removal_strategies>` za to, kako naj se izdelki odvzamejo "
"s te lokacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:106
msgid "Cyclic Counting section"
msgstr "Razdelek Ciklično štetje"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:108
msgid ""
"To schedule regular inventory counts at this location, set "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory Frequency (Days)` field to the desired interval. By "
"default, it is set to `0` (no scheduled counts)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite načrtovati redne inventurne popise na tej lokaciji, nastavite "
"polje :guilabel:`Pogostost inventure (dnevi)` na želeni interval. Privzeto "
"je nastavljeno na `0` (brez načrtovanih popisov)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:111
msgid ""
"For example, setting this field to `30`, schedules a count every thirty "
"days. For more specifics on setting up and using this feature, refer to "
"the :doc:`Cycle Counts documentation <cycle_counts>`."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če nastavite to polje na `30`, se štetje načrtuje vsakih trideset "
"dni. Za več podrobnosti o nastavitvi in uporabi te funkcije glejte "
":doc:`dokumentacijo o cikličnih popisih <cycle_counts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:114
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Last Effective Inventory` field displays the date the last "
"inventory count at this location occurred. When scheduled inventory counts "
"are enabled, the :guilabel:`Next Expected Inventory` field displays the date "
"of the next inventory count."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Zadnja dejanska inventura` prikazuje datum, ko je bil "
"izveden zadnji inventurni popis na tej lokaciji. Ko so načrtovani inventurni "
"popisi omogočeni, polje :guilabel:`Naslednja pričakovana inventura` "
"prikazuje datum naslednjega inventurnega popisa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:119
msgid ""
"With inventory counts scheduled to occur every `30` days, and "
"the :guilabel:`Last Effective Inventory` count occurring on July 16, "
"the :guilabel:`Next Expected Inventory` is August 15."
msgstr ""
"Ko so inventurni popisi načrtovani vsakih `30` dni in je bil popis "
":guilabel:`Zadnja dejanska inventura` izveden 16. julija, je "
":guilabel:`Naslednja pričakovana inventura` 15. avgusta."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:0
msgid "Show Cyclic Count section of the locations form."
msgstr "Prikaz razdelka Ciklično štetje obrazca lokacij."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:127
msgid "Logistics section"
msgstr "Razdelek logistike"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:129
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Logistics` section of the locations form, optionally "
"select a :guilabel:`Removal Strategy` to determine the order and priority of "
"how products are picked from inventory. The options are: :guilabel:`First In "
"First Out (FIFO)`, :guilabel:`Last In First Out (LIFO)`, :guilabel:`Closest "
"Location`, and :guilabel:`First Expiry First Out (FEFO)`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Logistika` na obrazcu lokacij po želji izberite "
":guilabel:`Strategijo odvzema`, da določite vrstni red in prednost, kako se "
"izdelki jemljejo iz zaloge. Možnosti so: :guilabel:`Prvi noter, prvi ven "
"(FIFO)`, :guilabel:`Zadnji noter, prvi ven (LIFO)`, :guilabel:`Najbližja "
"lokacija` in :guilabel:`Prvi poteče, prvi ven (FEFO)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:138
msgid "Current stock at location"
msgstr "Trenutna zaloga na lokaciji"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:140
msgid ""
"To view the current stock at a single location, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`, and "
"select the desired location."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled trenutne zaloge na posamezni lokaciji pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Lokacije` in izberite želeno "
"lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:143
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Current Stock` smart button to get a list of all "
"products at the location."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Trenutna zaloga`, da dobite seznam "
"vseh izdelkov na lokaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:147
msgid ""
"A list of current stock at `Shelf 1` consists of `266` cabinets and `39` "
"desks."
msgstr "Seznam trenutne zaloge na `Shelf 1` sestavlja `266` omaric in `39` miz."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/use_locations.rst:0
msgid "Show stock at Shelf 1."
msgstr "Prikaži zalogo na Polici 1."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the Odoo *Inventory* app, a *warehouse* is a physical space with an "
"address for storing items, such as a storage facility, distribution center, "
"or physical store."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji Odoo *Zaloga* je *skladišče* fizični prostor z naslovom za "
"shranjevanje artiklov, kot je skladiščni objekt, distribucijski center ali "
"fizična trgovina."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:8
msgid ""
"Each database has a pre-configured warehouse with the company's address. "
"Users can set up multiple warehouses, and :doc:`create stock moves <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes>` between them."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka podatkovna baza ima prednastavljeno skladišče z naslovom podjetja. "
"Uporabniki lahko nastavijo več skladišč in :doc:`ustvarijo premike zaloge "
"<../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/use_routes>` med njimi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:15
msgid ""
"To create or manage warehouses, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Warehouses`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje ali upravljanje skladišč pojdite na :menuselection:`Zaloga --"
"> Konfiguracija --> Skladišča`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:18
msgid ""
"Then, select an existing warehouse, or create a new one by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`. Doing so opens the warehouse form, which contains "
"the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite obstoječe skladišče ali ustvarite novega s klikom "
"na :guilabel:`Novo`. S tem se odpre obrazec skladišča, ki vsebuje naslednja "
"polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:21
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Warehouse` (*required field*): the full name of the warehouse."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skladišče` (*obvezno polje*): polno ime skladišča."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:22
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Short Name` (*required field*): the abbreviated code for the "
"warehouse (maximum five characters). The short name for the default "
"warehouse in Odoo is `WH`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kratko ime` (*obvezno polje*): okrajšana koda za skladišče "
"(največ pet znakov). Kratko ime privzetega skladišča v Odoo je `WH`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:26
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Short Name` appears on warehouse documents, so it is "
"recommended to use an memorable one, like \"WH[first letters of location]\" "
"(e.g. `WHA`, `WHB`, etc.)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Address` (*required field*): the address of the warehouse. To "
"change the warehouse address when creating two or more warehouses, hover "
"over the field, and click the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right "
"arrow)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naslov` (*obvezno polje*): naslov skladišča. Za spremembo naslova "
"skladišča pri ustvarjanju dveh ali več skladišč premaknite kazalec nad polje "
"in kliknite :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(puščica desno)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company` (*required field*): the company that owns the warehouse; "
"this can be set as the company that owns the Odoo database, or the company "
"of a customer or vendor."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podjetje` (*obvezno polje*): podjetje, ki je lastnik skladišča; "
"to je lahko podjetje, ki je lastnik podatkovne baze Odoo, ali podjetje "
"stranke ali dobavitelja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Intrastat region`: :doc:`region name <../../../../finance/"
"accounting/reporting/intrastat>` required for companies in the European "
"Union."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Regija Intrastat`: :doc:`ime regije <../../../../finance/"
"accounting/reporting/intrastat>`, zahtevano za podjetja v Evropski uniji."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:39
msgid ""
"The options below are available **only** when the *Multi-Step Routes* "
"feature is enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Spodnje možnosti so na voljo **samo**, ko je funkcija *Večstopenjske poti* "
"omogočena v :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Incoming Shipments`: select the option to receive products from "
"the warehouse in :doc:`one <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_one_step>`, :doc:`two <../../shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>`, or :doc:`three <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps>` steps."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dohodne pošiljke`: izberite možnost za prejemanje izdelkov iz "
"skladišča v :doc:`enem <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_one_step>`, :doc:`dveh <../../shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>` ali :doc:`treh <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/receipts_three_steps>` korakih."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:47
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Outgoing Shipments`: select the option to deliver products from "
"the warehouse in :doc:`one <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_one_step>`, :doc:`two <../../shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>`, or :doc:`three <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>` steps."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odhodne pošiljke`: izberite možnost za dostavo izdelkov iz "
"skladišča v :doc:`enem <../../shipping_receiving/daily_operations/"
"receipts_delivery_one_step>`, :doc:`dveh <../../shipping_receiving/"
"daily_operations/receipts_delivery_two_steps>` ali :doc:`treh <../../"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>` korakih."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dropship Subcontractors`: available with the *Subcontracting* "
"feature enabled in :menuselection:`Manufacturing app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Tick this checkbox to purchase components from vendors, and "
"dropship them to subcontractors."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Direktna dostava podizvajateljem`: na voljo z omogočeno funkcijo "
"*Podizvajanje* v :menuselection:`Proizvodnja --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`. Označite to polje za nakup komponent od dobaviteljev in njihovo "
"direktno dostavo podizvajateljem."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Resupply Subcontractors`: available with the *Subcontracting* "
"feature, tick this checkbox to supply subcontractors with raw materials "
"stored in *this* specific warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oskrba podizvajateljev`: na voljo z omogočeno funkcijo "
"*Podizvajanje*, označite to polje za oskrbo podizvajateljev s surovimi "
"materiali, shranjenimi v *tem* specifičnem skladišču."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manufacture to Resupply`: tick this checkbox to allow for items "
"to be manufactured in this warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Proizvodnja za oskrbo`: označite to polje, da omogočite "
"proizvodnjo artiklov v tem skladišču."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manufacture`: choose whether to manufacture products in :doc:`one "
"<../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/one_step_manufacturing>`, :doc:`two "
"<../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/two_step_manufacturing>`, or :doc:`three "
"steps <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/three_step_manufacturing>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Proizvedi`: izberite, ali želite proizvajati izdelke v :doc:`enem "
"<../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/one_step_manufacturing>`, :doc:`dveh "
"<../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/two_step_manufacturing>` ali :doc:`treh "
"korakih <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/three_step_manufacturing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy to Resupply`: tick this checkbox to allow for purchased "
"products to be delivered to the warehouse."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kupi za dopolnitev`: označite to potrditveno polje, če želite "
"omogočiti dostavo kupljenih izdelkov v skladišče."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Resupply From`: available with multiple warehouses in the "
"database, select warehouses to pull stock *from* to fulfill orders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dopolni iz`: na voljo pri več skladiščih v bazi podatkov, "
"izberite skladišča, iz katerih naj se *potegne* zaloga za izpolnitev nalogov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:69
msgid ""
":doc:`Use inventory adjustments to add stock to new warehouses "
"<count_products>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Za dodajanje zaloge v nova skladišča uporabite popravke zaloge "
"<count_products>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses.rst:None
msgid "Example warehouse form."
msgstr "Primer obrazca skladišča."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:15
msgid ""
"In Odoo, stock can be replenished one of three ways: *reordering rules*, the "
"*make to order* (MTO) route, or using the *master production schedule* (MPS)."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo je mogoče zalogo dopolnjevati na enega od treh načinov: *pravila "
"prenaročanja*, smer *naredi na naročilo* (MTO) ali z uporabo *glavnega "
"proizvodnega načrta* (MPS)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:18
msgid ""
"Each replenishment mechanism triggers the creation or suggestion of a "
"purchase order (PO) or manufacturing order (MO), with the best choice "
"depending on the business process."
msgstr ""
"Vsak mehanizem dopolnjevanja sproži ustvarjanje ali predlog nabavnega naloga "
"(PO) ali proizvodnega naloga (MO), pri čemer je najboljša izbira odvisna od "
"poslovnega procesa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:3
msgid "Reordering rules"
msgstr "Pravila za ponovno naročanje"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:23
msgid ""
"Automatically suggest or generate POs or MOs when stock falls below a "
"minimum level."
msgstr ""
"Automaticky navrhnout nebo vygenerovat nákupní nebo výrobní příkazy, když "
"zásoby klesnou pod minimální úroveň."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:23
msgid "Recommended"
msgstr "Doporučeno"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses.rst:81
msgid "MTO"
msgstr "MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:30
msgid "Automatically generate POs or MOs when sales orders are confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Automaticky generovat nákupní nebo výrobní příkazy při potvrzení prodejních "
"objednávek."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:30
msgid "Beginner-friendly"
msgstr "Vhodné pro začátečníky"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:36
msgid "MPS"
msgstr "MPS"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:36
msgid ""
"Manage long-term replenishment based on inputted sales forecasts, via a "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Spravujte dlouhodobé doplňování zásob na základě zadaných prodejních prognóz "
"prostřednictvím nadzorné plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:42
msgid "Replenishment strategies"
msgstr "Strategije dopolnjevanja"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:45
msgid "Replenishment report and reordering rules"
msgstr "Poročilo o dopolnjevanju in pravila prenaročanja"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:47
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are rules that can be set up to maintain a minimum stock "
"level. They are often configured to support manufacturing or sales "
"requirements. When a product's stock falls at or below the minimum level, "
"Odoo generates (or suggests) a purchase or manufacturing order to replenish "
"stock to the maximum level."
msgstr ""
"Pravila prenaročanja so pravila, ki jih je mogoče nastaviti za vzdrževanje "
"minimalne ravni zaloge. Pogosto so konfigurirana za podporo proizvodnim ali "
"prodajnim zahtevam. Ko zaloga izdelka pade na minimalno raven ali pod njo, "
"Odoo ustvari (ali predlaga) nabavni ali proizvodni nalog za dopolnitev "
"zaloge do maksimalne ravni."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:52
msgid ""
"When using automatic reordering rules, Odoo generates a new order. When "
"using manual, Odoo suggests orders on the replenishment report. For detailed "
"guidance, refer to the :doc:`replenishment report <replenishment/report>` "
"and :doc:`reordering rules <replenishment/reordering_rules>`."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi samodejnih pravil prenaročanja Odoo ustvari nov nalog. Pri "
"uporabi ročnih Odoo predlaga naloge v poročilu o dopolnjevanju. Za podrobna "
"navodila glejte :doc:`poročilo o dopolnjevanju <replenishment/report>` "
"in :doc:`pravila prenaročanja <replenishment/reordering_rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:56
msgid "Key points include:"
msgstr "Ključne točke vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:58
msgid ""
":ref:`Automatic reordering rules <inventory/warehouses_storage/auto-rr>`: "
"Automatically create |POs| or |MOs| when stock falls below the minimum "
"level. While this is convenient, it is less flexible."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Samodejno pravilo prenaročanja <inventory/warehouses_storage/auto-"
"rr>`: Samodejno ustvari |POs| ali |MOs|, ko zaloga pade pod minimalno raven. "
"Čeprav je to priročno, je manj prilagodljivo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:61
msgid ""
":ref:`Manual reordering rules <inventory/warehouses_storage/manual-rr>`: "
"Generate suggestions in the replenishment report for user review, allowing "
"adjustments and batch orders while meeting deadlines."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ročna pravila prenaročanja <inventory/warehouses_storage/manual-rr>`: "
"Ustvarijo predloge v poročilu o dopolnjevanju za pregled uporabnika, kar "
"omogoča prilagoditve in skupinske naloge ob upoštevanju rokov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:64
msgid ""
":ref:`Just-in-time logic <inventory/warehouses_storage/just-in-time>`: A "
"strategy to replenish only what is needed to prevent overstocking."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Logika pravočasno <inventory/warehouses_storage/just-in-time>`: "
"strategija za dopolnjevanje samo tistega, kar je potrebno, da se prepreči "
"prekomerno zalaganje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:68
msgid ":doc:`replenishment/reordering_rules`"
msgstr ":doc:`replenishment/reordering_rules`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:69
msgid ":doc:`replenishment/report`"
msgstr ":doc:`replenishment/report`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:74
msgid "Make to order"
msgstr "Naredi na naročilo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:76
msgid ""
"An |MTO| strategy means that procurement or production is triggered only "
"after a sales order has been confirmed. This strategy is recommended when "
"products are customizable, demand is unpredictable, there is limited storage "
"capacity, and when products are high in value and low in demand. In such "
"cases, it does not make sense to keep on-hand inventory."
msgstr ""
"Strategija |MTO| pomeni, da se oskrba ali proizvodnja sproži šele po "
"potrditvi prodajnega naloga. Ta strategija je priporočljiva, ko so izdelki "
"prilagodljivi, je povpraševanje nepredvidljivo, je skladiščna kapaciteta "
"omejena in ko so izdelki visoke vrednosti in nizkega povpraševanja. V takih "
"primerih nima smisla vzdrževati zaloge na zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:81
msgid ""
"Unlike products replenished using reordering rules, Odoo automatically links "
"the sales order to the |PO| or |MO| generated by the |MTO| route."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od izdelkov, dopolnjenih z uporabo pravil prenaročanja, Odoo "
"samodejno poveže prodajni nalog z |PO| ali |MO|, ustvarjenim s smerjo |MTO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:84
msgid ""
"Another difference between reordering rules and |MTO| is, with |MTO|, Odoo "
"generates a draft |PO| or |MO| immediately after the |SO| is confirmed. With "
"reordering rules, Odoo generates a draft |PO| or |MO| when the product's "
"forecasted stock falls below the set minimum quantity."
msgstr ""
"Druga razlika med pravili prenaročanja in |MTO| je, da Odoo pri |MTO| "
"ustvari osnutek |PO| ali |MO| takoj po potrditvi |SO|. Pri pravilih "
"prenaročanja Odoo ustvari osnutek |PO| ali |MO|, ko predvidena zaloga "
"izdelka pade pod določeno minimalno količino."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:88
msgid ""
"In addition, Odoo automatically adds quantities to the |PO| or |MO| as the "
"forecast changes, so long as the |PO| or |MO| is not confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega Odoo samodejno dodaja količine v |PO| ali |MO|, ko se napoved "
"spreminja, dokler |PO| ali |MO| ni potrjen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:91
msgid ""
"The |MTO| route is the best replenishment strategy for products that are "
"customized, and/or for products that have no stock kept on-hand."
msgstr ""
"Pot |MTO| je najboljša strategija dopolnjevanja za izdelke, ki so "
"prilagojeni, in/ali za izdelke, za katere se ne vzdržuje zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:95
msgid ":doc:`replenishment/mto`"
msgstr ":doc:`replenishment/mto`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/workflows/use_mps.rst:3
msgid "Master production schedule"
msgstr "Glavni proizvodni načrt"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:100
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`MPS (Master Production Schedule)` is a dashboard where products "
"and their forecasted quantities are entered. Based on confirmed "
"manufacturing and purchase orders, the dashboard recommends amounts to order "
"or produce."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`MPS (glavni proizvodni načrt)` je nadzorna plošča, kamor se vnašajo "
"izdelki in njihove predvidene količine. Na podlagi potrjenih proizvodnih in "
"nabavnih naročil nadzorna plošča priporoča količine za naročilo ali "
"proizvodnjo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:104
msgid ""
"This a useful **manual** tool for keeping track of quantities. "
"The :abbr:`MPS (Master Production Schedule)` **should absolutely not** be "
"used alongside reordering rules, as the automated workflow disrupts its "
"manual replenishment method."
msgstr ""
"To je uporabno **ročno** orodje za spremljanje količin. :abbr:`MPS (glavni "
"proizvodni načrt)` **se nikakor ne sme** uporabljati skupaj s pravili za "
"ponovno naročanje, saj avtomatizirani potek dela moti njegovo ročno metodo "
"dopolnjevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment.rst:109
msgid ":doc:`../../manufacturing/workflows/use_mps`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../manufacturing/workflows/use_mps`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:3
msgid "Lead times"
msgstr "Dobavni roki"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:11
msgid ""
"Accurately forecasting delivery dates is vital for fulfilling customer "
"expectations. In Odoo, the **Inventory** app allows for comprehensive lead "
"time configuration, allowing coordination and planning of manufacturing "
"orders, deliveries, and receipts."
msgstr ""
"Natančno napovedovanje datumov dostave je ključnega pomena za izpolnjevanje "
"pričakovanj strank. V Odoo aplikacija **Zaloga** omogoča celovito "
"konfiguracijo dobavnih rokov, kar omogoča usklajevanje in načrtovanje "
"proizvodnih nalogov, dostav in prejemov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:16
msgid "Lead time types"
msgstr "Vrste dobavnih rokov"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:18
msgid ""
"Different lead times for different operations can impact various stages of "
"the order fulfillment process. Here's a summary of the types of lead times "
"in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Različni dobavni roki za različne operacije lahko vplivajo na različne faze "
"procesa izpolnjevanja naročila. Tukaj je povzetek vrst dobavnih rokov v Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid "Show graphic of all lead times working together."
msgstr "Prikaz grafike vseh dobavnih rokov, ki delujejo skupaj."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:24
msgid ""
":ref:`Customer lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/customer-lt>`: "
"default time frame for fulfilling customer orders. The customer lead time is "
"the number of days from the date the sales order (SO) is confirmed to the "
"date the products are shipped from the warehouse. This is also known as "
"*delivery lead time*."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dobavni rok stranki <inventory/warehouses_storage/customer-lt>`: "
"privzeti časovni okvir za izpolnjevanje naročil strank. Dobavni rok stranki "
"je število dni od datuma potrditve prodajnega naloga do datuma odpreme "
"izdelkov iz skladišča. To je znano tudi kot *dobavni rok*."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:29
msgid ""
":ref:`Sales security lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/sales-security-"
"lt>`: moves the *scheduled delivery date* forward by a specified number of "
"days. This serves as a buffer to allow ample time to prepare the outgoing "
"shipment earlier, considering the possibility of delays in the fulfillment "
"process."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Varnostni rok prodaje <inventory/warehouses_storage/sales-security-lt>"
"`: prestavi *načrtovani datum dostave* naprej za določeno število dni. To "
"služi kot medpomnilnik, ki omogoča dovolj časa za pripravo odhodne pošiljke "
"prej, ob upoštevanju možnosti zamud v procesu izpolnjevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:34
msgid ""
":ref:`Purchase lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/purchase-lt>`: number "
"of days from the confirmation of a purchase order (PO) to the receipt of "
"products. It provides insight on the time it takes for products to arrive at "
"the warehouse, facilitating effective scheduling and planning of supplier "
"deliveries."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dobavni rok nabave <inventory/warehouses_storage/purchase-lt>`: "
"število dni od potrditve nabavnega naloga do prejema izdelkov. Zagotavlja "
"vpogled v čas, ki je potreben, da izdelki prispejo v skladišče, kar omogoča "
"učinkovito razporejanje in načrtovanje dobav dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:39
msgid ""
":ref:`Purchase security lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/purchase-"
"security-lt>`: advances the order deadline on a :abbr:`PO (Purchase Order)` "
"by a specified number of days. This proactive approach of placing orders "
"earlier mitigates the risk of vendor or shipping delays. Thus, for products "
"that are set to replenish to order, the need appears on the *Replenishment "
"report* earlier, according to the specified number of days."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Varnostni rok nabave <inventory/warehouses_storage/purchase-security-"
"lt>`: prestavi rok za naročilo pri :abbr:`NN (nabavnem nalogu)` naprej za "
"določeno število dni. Ta proaktiven pristop zgodnejšega oddajanja naročil "
"zmanjšuje tveganje zamud dobavitelja ali pošiljanja. Tako se pri izdelkih, "
"ki so nastavljeni na dopolnjevanje po naročilu, potreba pojavi na *Poročilu "
"o dopolnjevanju* prej, v skladu z določenim številom dni."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:45
msgid ""
":ref:`Days to Purchase <inventory/warehouses_storage/days-to-purchase>`: "
"days needed for the vendor to receive a request for quotation (RFQ) and "
"confirm it. It advances the deadline to schedule a |RFQ| by a specified "
"number of days."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dni do nakupa <inventory/warehouses_storage/days-to-purchase>`: dnevi, "
"ki jih dobavitelj potrebuje za prejem zahteve za ponudbo (RFQ) in njeno "
"potrditev. Prestavi rok za razporeditev |RFQ| naprej za določeno število dni."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:49
msgid ""
":ref:`Manufacturing lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/manuf-lt>`: "
"number of days needed to complete a manufacturing order (MO) from the date "
"of confirmation. This lead time includes weekends (non-working hours in "
"Odoo), and is used to forecast an approximate production date for a finished "
"good."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dobavni rok proizvodnje <inventory/warehouses_storage/manuf-lt>`: "
"število dni, potrebnih za dokončanje proizvodnega naloga od datuma "
"potrditve. Ta dobavni rok vključuje vikende (nedelovne ure v Odoo) in se "
"uporablja za napovedovanje približnega datuma proizvodnje za končni izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:54
msgid ""
":ref:`Days to prepare manufacturing order <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"prepare-manufacturing-order>`: number of days needed to replenish "
"components, or manufacture sub-assemblies of the product. Either set one "
"directly on the bill of materials (BoM), or click *Compute* to sum up "
"purchase and manufacturing lead times of components in the |BoM|."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dnevi za pripravo proizvodnega naloga <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"prepare-manufacturing-order>`: število dni, potrebnih za dopolnitev "
"komponent ali proizvodnjo podsestav izdelka. Nastavite jih neposredno v "
"recepturi ali kliknite *Izračunaj*, da seštejete dobavne roke nabave in "
"proizvodnje komponent v |BoM|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:60
msgid ""
":ref:`Manufacturing security lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/manuf-"
"security-lt>`: moves the scheduled date of the |MO| forward by a specified "
"number of days. When used in conjunction with :ref:`replenish to order "
"<inventory/management/products/strategies>`, the security lead time makes "
"the need appear earlier on the replenishment report."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Varnostni rok proizvodnje <inventory/warehouses_storage/manuf-security-"
"lt>`: prestavi načrtovani datum |MO| naprej za določeno število dni. Kadar "
"se uporablja skupaj z :ref:`dopolnjevanjem po naročilu <inventory/management/"
"products/strategies>`, varnostni rok povzroči, da se potreba pojavi prej na "
"poročilu o dopolnjevanju."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:68
msgid "Sales lead times"
msgstr "Dobavni roki pri prodaji"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:70
msgid ""
"Customer lead times and sales security lead times can be configured to "
"automatically compute an *expected delivery date* on a :abbr:`SO (Sales "
"Order)`. The expected delivery date ensures a realistic *delivery dates* "
"setting for shipments from the warehouse."
msgstr ""
"Dobavni roki za stranke in varnostni dobavni roki prodaje se lahko "
"konfigurirajo za samodejno izračunavanje *pričakovanega datuma dostave* na "
":abbr:`prodajnem nalogu (PN)`. Pričakovani datum dostave zagotavlja "
"realistično nastavitev *datumov dostave* za pošiljke iz skladišča."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:74
msgid ""
"Odoo issues a warning message if the set delivery date is earlier than the "
"expected date, as it may not be feasible to fulfill the order by that time, "
"which would impact other warehouse operations."
msgstr ""
"Odoo izda opozorilno sporočilo, če je nastavljeni datum dobave zgodnejši od "
"pričakovanega datuma, saj morda ne bo mogoče izpolniti naročila do takrat, "
"kar bi vplivalo na druge skladiščne operacije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:78
msgid ""
"A :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` containing a `Coconut-scented candle` is "
"confirmed on July 11th. The product has a customer lead time of 14 days, and "
"the business uses a sales security lead time of 1 day. Based on the lead "
"time inputs, Odoo suggests a delivery date in 15 days, on July 26th."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid ""
"Set *Delivery Date* in a sales order. Enables delivery lead times feature."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite *Datum dostave* v prodajnem nalogu. Omogoči funkcijo dobavnih "
"rokov dostave."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:85
msgid ""
"The following sections demonstrate how to automatically compute expected "
"delivery dates."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji razdelki prikazujejo, kako samodejno izračunati pričakovane datume "
"dostave."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:88
msgid "Customer lead time"
msgstr "Dobavni rok za stranko"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:90
msgid ""
"Set the customer lead time on each product form, by navigating to the "
"products page. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products`. From there, select the desired product, and switch to "
"the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab. Then, under the :guilabel:`Customer Lead "
"Time` field, fill in the number of calendar days required to fulfill the "
"delivery order from start to finish."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite dobavni rok za stranko na vsakem obrazcu izdelka, tako da se "
"pomaknete na stran izdelkov. Za to pojdite na :menuselection:`aplikacija "
"Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`. Od tam izberite želeni izdelek in "
"preklopite na zavihek :guilabel:`Zaloga`. Nato v polje :guilabel:`Dobavni "
"rok za stranko` vnesite število koledarskih dni, potrebnih za izpolnitev "
"dobavnega naročila od začetka do konca."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:96
msgid ""
"Set a 14-day customer lead time for the `Coconut-scented candle` by "
"navigating to its product form. Then, in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, type "
"`14.00` days into the :guilabel:`Customer Lead Time` field."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite 14-dnevni dobavni rok za stranko za `Sveča z vonjem po kokosu` "
"tako, da se pomaknete na obrazec izdelka. Nato na zavihku :guilabel:`Zaloga` "
"v polje :guilabel:`Dobavni rok za stranko` vnesite `14.00` dni."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid "Set *Customer Lead Time* on the product form."
msgstr "Nastavite *Dobavni rok za stranko* na obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:106
msgid "Sales security lead time"
msgstr "Varnostni dobavni rok za prodajo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:108
msgid ""
"*Sales security lead time* is set globally for the business "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"*Varnostni dobavni rok prodaje* je nastavljen globalno za podjetje v "
":menuselection:`aplikacija Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:111
msgid ""
"On the configuration page, under the :guilabel:`Advanced Scheduling` "
"heading, locate the box for :guilabel:`Security Lead Time for Sales`, and "
"click the checkbox to enable the feature."
msgstr ""
"Na konfiguracijski strani pod naslovom :guilabel:`Napredno načrtovanje` "
"poiščite polje za :guilabel:`Varnostni dobavni rok za prodajo` in kliknite "
"potrditveno polje za omogočitev funkcije."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:114
msgid ""
"Next, enter the desired number of calendar days. This security lead time is "
"a buffer notifying the team to prepare for outgoing shipments earlier than "
"the scheduled date."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite želeno število koledarskih dni. Ta varnostni dobavni rok je "
"blažilnik, ki ekipo obvesti, naj se pripravi na odhodne pošiljke prej kot na "
"načrtovani datum."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:118
msgid ""
"Setting the :guilabel:`Security Lead Time for Sales` to `1.00` day, pushes "
"the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` of a delivery order (DO) forward by one day. "
"In that case, if a product is initially scheduled for delivery on April 6th, "
"but with a one-day security lead time, the new scheduled date for the "
"delivery order would be April 5th."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev :guilabel:`Varnostni dobavni rok za prodajo` na `1.00` dan "
"premakne :guilabel:`Načrtovani datum` dobavnega naložba (DO) naprej za en "
"dan. V tem primeru, če je izdelek sprva načrtovan za dobavo 6. aprila, "
"vendar z enodnevnim varnostnim dobavnim rokom, bo nov načrtovani datum za "
"dobavni nalog 5. april."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of the security lead time for sales configuration from the sales "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Pogled nastavitve varnostnega dobavnega roka za prodajo v nastavitvah "
"prodaje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:127
msgid "Deliver several products"
msgstr "Dostavljanje več izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:129
msgid ""
"For orders that include multiple products with different lead times, the "
"lead times can be configured directly from the quotation itself. On a "
"quotation, click the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, and set "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Policy` to:"
msgstr ""
"Za naročila, ki vključujejo več izdelkov z različnimi dobavnimi roki, je "
"mogoče dobavne roke konfigurirati neposredno iz ponudbe. V ponudbi kliknite "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Druge informacije` in nastavite :guilabel:`Politika "
"dostave` na:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`As soon as possible` to deliver products as soon as they are "
"ready. The :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` of the :abbr:`DO (Delivery Order)` is "
"determined by adding today's date to the shortest lead time among the "
"products in the order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Takoj, ko je mogoče`, za dostavo izdelkov takoj, ko so "
"pripravljeni. :guilabel:`Načrtovani datum` :abbr:`DO (naročilnica za dostavo)"
"` se določi z dodajanjem današnjega datuma najkrajšemu dobavnemu roku med "
"izdelki v naročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`When all products are ready` to wait to fulfill the entire order "
"at once. The :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` of the :abbr:`DO (Delivery Order)` "
"is determined by adding today's date to the longest lead time among the "
"products in the order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ko so vsi izdelki pripravljeni`, da počaka na izpolnitev "
"celotnega naročila naenkrat. :guilabel:`Načrtovani datum` :abbr:`DO (dobavni "
"nalog)` se določi tako, da se današnjemu datumu prišteje najdaljši dobavni "
"rok med izdelki v naročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid "Show *Shipping Policy* field in the *Other Info* tab of a quotation."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz polja *Pravilnik o pošiljanju* na zavihku *Ostale informacije* "
"ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:145
msgid ""
"In a quotation containing 2 products, `Yoga mat` and `Resistance band,` the "
"products have a lead time of 8 days and 5 days, respectively. Today's date "
"is April 2nd."
msgstr ""
"V ponudbi, ki vsebuje 2 izdelka, `Podloga za jogo` in `Elastični trak`, "
"imata izdelka dobavni rok 8 dni oziroma 5 dni. Današnji datum je 2. april."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:148
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Shipping Policy` is set to :guilabel:`As soon as "
"possible`, the scheduled delivery date is 5 days from today: April 7th. On "
"the other hand, selecting :guilabel:`When all products are ready` configures "
"the scheduled date to be 8 days from today: April 10th."
msgstr ""
"Ko je :guilabel:`Pravilnik o pošiljanju` nastavljen na :guilabel:`Čim prej`, "
"je načrtovani datum dobave 5 dni od danes: 7. april. Po drugi strani pa "
"izbira :guilabel:`Ko so vsi izdelki pripravljeni` nastavi načrtovani datum "
"na 8 dni od danes: 10. april."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:155
msgid "Purchase lead times"
msgstr "Dobavni roki nabave"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:157
msgid ""
"Automatically determining the dates on which to place orders from suppliers "
"can help simplify the procurement process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:160
msgid ""
"Odoo calculates the supplier shipment *receipt date*, and :abbr:`PO "
"(Purchase Order)` deadline, based on the required date the product is needed "
"in the warehouse. By working backwards from the receipt date, vendor lead "
"times and purchase security lead times are taken into account, in order to "
"determine the :abbr:`PO (Purchase Order)` deadline."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:165
msgid ""
"This deadline is the date by which the order should be confirmed, in order "
"to ensure timely arrival by the expected receipt date."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid ""
"Visualization of PO deadline and receipt date used with vendor lead times."
msgstr ""
"Vizualizacija roka naročilnice in datuma prejema, uporabljenega z dobavnimi "
"roki dobavitelja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:172
msgid ":doc:`PO scheduling with reordering rules <reordering_rules>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Načrtovanje naročilnic s pravili za ponovno naročanje "
"<reordering_rules>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:175
msgid "Vendor lead time"
msgstr "Dobavni rok dobavitelja"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:177
msgid ""
"To set a vendor lead time for orders arriving in the warehouse from a vendor "
"location, begin by navigating to a product form "
"through :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products --> Products`."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev dobavnega roka dobavitelja za naročila, ki prispejo v "
"skladišče iz lokacije dobavitelja, začnite z navigacijo na obrazec izdelka "
"prek :menuselection:`Aplikacija za nabavo --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:180
msgid ""
"Next, select the desired product, and switch to the :guilabel:`Purchase` "
"tab. In the editable vendor pricelist, click the :guilabel:`Add a line` "
"button to add vendor details, such as the :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"name, :guilabel:`Price` offered for the product, and lastly, "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Lead Time`."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite želeni izdelek in preklopite na zavihek :guilabel:`Nakup`. V "
"urejevalnem ceniku dobavitelja kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da "
"dodate podrobnosti dobavitelja, kot so ime :guilabel:`Dobavitelj`, "
":guilabel:`Cena`, ponujena za izdelek, in nazadnje :guilabel:`Dobavni rok`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:186
msgid ""
"Multiple vendors and lead times can be added to the vendor pricelist. The "
"default vendor and lead time selected will be the entry at the top of the "
"list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:190
msgid ""
"On the vendor pricelist of the product form, the :guilabel:`Delivery Lead "
"Time` for the selected vendor is set to `10 days.`"
msgstr ""
"V ceniku dobavitelja na obrazcu izdelka je :guilabel:`Dobavni rok` za "
"izbranega dobavitelja nastavljen na `10 dni.`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid "Add delivery lead times to vendor pricelist on a product."
msgstr "Dodajanje dobavnih rokov v cenik dobavitelja na izdelku."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:196
msgid ""
"By setting the vendor lead time, the expected arrival date of the item is "
"automatically determined as the date of the :abbr:`PO (Purchase Order)` "
"confirmation, plus the vendor lead time. This ensures that warehouse "
"employees are notified, if the products do **not** arrive within the "
"expected timeframe."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:202
msgid ""
"On a :abbr:`PO (Purchase Order)` confirmed on July 11th, for a product "
"configured with a 10-day vendor lead time, Odoo automatically sets "
"the :guilabel:`Receipt Date` to July 21st. The receipt date also appears as "
"the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` on the warehouse receipt form, accessible "
"from the :guilabel:`Receipt` smart button, located on the :guilabel:`PO "
"(Purchase Order)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid "Show expected *Receipt Date* of the product from the vendor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid ""
"Show expected *Scheduled Date* of arrival of the product from the vendor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:216
msgid "Purchase security lead time"
msgstr "Varnostni dobavni rok za nakup"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:218
msgid ""
"*Purchase security lead time* is set globally for the business "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:221
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, under the :guilabel:`Advanced Scheduling` "
"heading, tick the checkbox for :guilabel:`Security Lead Time for Purchase`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:224
msgid ""
"Next, enter the desired number of calendar days. By configuring the security "
"lead time, a buffer is set to account for potential delays in supplier "
"deliveries. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite želeno število koledarskih dni. S konfiguracijo varnostnega "
"dobavnega roka nastavite blažilnik za morebitne zamude pri dobavah "
"dobaviteljev. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:228
msgid ""
"Setting the :guilabel:`Security Lead Time for Purchase` to `2.00` days, "
"pushes the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` of receipt back by two days. In that "
"case, if a product is initially scheduled to arrive on April 6th, with a two-"
"day security lead time, the new scheduled date for the receipt would be "
"April 8th."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:0
msgid ""
"Set security lead time for purchase from the Inventory > Configuration > "
"Settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:239
msgid "Days to purchase lead time"
msgstr "Dobavna roka za dneve do nakupa"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:241
msgid ""
"To set it up, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Advanced Scheduling` section, in "
"the :guilabel:`Days to Purchase` field, specify the number of days required "
"for the vendor to confirm a |RFQ| after receiving it from the company."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev pojdite na :menuselection:`aplikacija Zaloga --> Konfiguracija "
"--> Nastavitve`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Napredno načrtovanje`, v "
"polje :guilabel:`Dnevi do nakupa`, določite število dni, potrebnih za "
"potrditev |RFQ| s strani dobavitelja po prejemu od podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:248
msgid "Manufacturing lead times"
msgstr "Dobavni roki proizvodnje"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:250
msgid ""
"Lead times can help simplify the procurement process for consumable "
"materials and components used in manufactured products with bills of "
"materials (BoMs)."
msgstr ""
"Dobavni roki lahko pomagajo poenostaviti postopek nabave potrošnega "
"materiala in komponent, uporabljenih v proizvedenih izdelkih s seznami "
"materialov (BoMs)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:253
msgid ""
"The |MO| deadline, which is the deadline to begin the manufacturing process "
"to complete the product by the scheduled delivery date, can be determined by "
"configuring the manufacturing lead times and manufacturing security lead "
"times."
msgstr ""
"Rok |MO|, ki je rok za začetek proizvodnega procesa za dokončanje izdelka do "
"načrtovanega datuma dobave, je mogoče določiti s konfiguracijo dobavnih "
"rokov proizvodnje in varnostnih dobavnih rokov proizvodnje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid ""
"Visualization of the determination of planned MO date manufacturing lead "
"times."
msgstr ""
"Vizualizacija določanja načrtovanega datuma MO z dobavnimi roki proizvodnje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:261
msgid "Manufacturing lead time"
msgstr "Proizvodni dobavni rok"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:263
msgid ""
"Manufacturing lead times for products are configured from a product's bill "
"of materials (BoM) form."
msgstr ""
"Proizvodni dobavni roki za izdelke so nastavljeni na obrazcu kosovnice (BoM) "
"izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:265
msgid ""
"To add a lead time to a |BoM|, navigate to :menuselection:`Manufacturing app "
"--> Products --> Bills of Materials`, and select the desired |BoM| to edit."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati dobavni rok |BoM|, pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Proizvodnja --> Izdelki --> Kosovnice` in izberite želeno |BoM| za urejanje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:268
msgid ""
"On the |BoM| form, click the :guilabel:`Miscellaneous` tab. Change the value "
"(in days) in the :guilabel:`Manuf. Lead Time` field to specify the calendar "
"days needed to manufacture the product."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu |BoM| kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Razno`. Spremenite vrednost (v "
"dnevih) v polju :guilabel:`Proizvodni dobavni rok`, da določite koledarske "
"dneve, potrebne za proizvodnjo izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid "Manuf. Lead Time value specified on a product's Bill of Material form."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost proizvodnega dobavnega roka, določena na obrazcu kosovnice izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:275
msgid ""
"If the selected |BoM| is a multi-level |BoM|, the manufacturing lead times "
"of the components are added."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana |BoM| večnivojska |BoM|, se proizvodni dobavni roki komponent "
"seštejejo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:278
msgid ""
"If the |BoM| product is subcontracted, the :guilabel:`Manuf. Lead Time` can "
"be used to determine the date at which components should be sent to the "
"subcontractor."
msgstr ""
"Če je izdelek |BoM| poddodan, se lahko :guilabel:`Proizvodni dobavni rok` "
"uporabi za določitev datuma, na katerega je treba komponente poslati "
"podizvajalncu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:281
msgid ""
"Establish a |MO| deadline, based on the *expected delivery date*, indicated "
"in the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` field of the :abbr:`DO (Delivery Order)`."
msgstr ""
"Določite rok |MO| na podlagi *pričakovanega datuma dostave*, navedenega v "
"polju :guilabel:`Načrtovan datum` :abbr:`DO (naročilnica za dostavo)`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:284
msgid ""
"The |MO| deadline, which is the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` field on the |"
"MO|, is calculated as the *expected delivery date* subtracted by the "
"manufacturing lead time."
msgstr ""
"Rok |MO|, ki je polje :guilabel:`Načrtovan datum` na |MO|, se izračuna kot "
"*pričakovan datum dostave* minus proizvodni dobavni rok."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:287
msgid ""
"This ensures the manufacturing process begins on time, in order to meet the "
"delivery date."
msgstr ""
"To zagotavlja, da se proizvodni proces začne pravočasno, da se izpolni datum "
"dostave."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:289
msgid ""
"However, it is important to note that lead times are based on calendar days. "
"Lead times do **not** consider weekends, holidays, or *work center capacity* "
"(:dfn:`the number of operations that can be performed at the work center "
"simultaneously`)."
msgstr ""
"Vendar je pomembno opozoriti, da temeljijo dobavni roki na koledarskih "
"dnevih. Dobavni roki **ne** upoštevajo vikendov, praznikov ali *zmogljivosti "
"delovnega centra* (:dfn:`število operacij, ki jih je mogoče izvesti v "
"delovnem centru hkrati`)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:294
msgid ""
":doc:`Manufacturing planning <../../../manufacturing/workflows/use_mps>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Načrtovanje proizvodnje <../../../manufacturing/workflows/use_mps>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:295
msgid ":doc:`Schedule MOs with reordering rules <reordering_rules>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Načrtujte proizvodne naloge s pravili ponovnega naročanja "
"<reordering_rules>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:298
msgid ""
"A product's scheduled shipment date on the :abbr:`DO (Delivery Order)` is "
"August 15th. The product requires 14 days to manufacture. So, the latest "
"date to start the :abbr:`MO (Manufacturing Order)` to meet the commitment "
"date is August 1st."
msgstr ""
"Načrtovan datum odpreme izdelka na :abbr:`DO (naročilnici za dostavo)` je "
"15. avgust. Izdelek zahteva 14 dni za proizvodnjo. Torej je zadnji datum za "
"začetek :abbr:`MO (proizvodnega naloga)`, da se izpolni rok, 1. avgust."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:305
msgid "Days to prepare manufacturing order"
msgstr "Dnevi za pripravo proizvodnega naloga"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:307
msgid ""
"Configure the days required to gather components to manufacture a product by "
"going to its |BoM|. To do that, go to :menuselection:`Manufacturing app --> "
"Products --> Bills of Materials`, and select the desired |BoM|."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte dni, potrebne za zbiranje komponent za proizvodnjo izdelka, "
"tako da greste na njegov |BoM|. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija za proizvodnjo --> Izdelki --> Kosalovnice` in "
"izberete želeno |BoM|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:311
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Miscellaneous` tab of the |BoM|, specify the calendar days "
"needed to obtain components of the product in the :guilabel:`Days to prepare "
"Manufacturing Order` field. Doing so creates |MOs| in advance, and ensures "
"there is enough time to either replenish components, or manufacture semi-"
"finished products."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Razno` |BoM| navedite koledarske dni, potrebne za "
"pridobitev komponent izdelka, v polju :guilabel:`Dnevi za pripravo "
"proizvodnega naloga`. S tem vnaprej ustvarite |MOs| in zagotovite dovolj "
"časa za dopolnitev komponent ali proizvodnjo polizdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:317
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Compute`, located next to the :guilabel:`Days to prepare "
"Manufacturing Order` field, calculates the longest lead time among all the "
"components listed on the |BoM|."
msgstr ""
"Klik na :guilabel:`Izračunaj`, ki se nahaja poleg polja :guilabel:`Dnevi za "
"pripravo proizvodnega naloga`, izračuna najdaljši dobavni rok med vsemi "
"komponentami, navedenimi na |BoM|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:320
msgid ""
"*Purchase security lead times* that impact this specific |BoM| are also "
"added to this value."
msgstr ""
"*Varnostni dobavni roki za nakup*, ki vplivajo na ta specifični |BoM|, se "
"prav tako dodajo tej vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:324
msgid ""
"A |BoM| has two components, one has a manufacturing lead time of two days, "
"and the other has a purchase lead time of four days. The :guilabel:`Days to "
"prepare Manufacturing Order` is four days."
msgstr ""
"|BoM| ima dve komponenti, ena ima proizvodni dobavni rok dva dni, druga pa "
"ima dobavni rok za nakup štiri dni. :guilabel:`Dnevi za pripravo "
"proizvodnega naloga` so štirje dnevi."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:331
msgid "Manufacturing security lead time"
msgstr "Varnostni dobavni rok za proizvodnjo"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:333
msgid ""
"*Manufacturing security lead time* is set globally for the business "
"in :menuselection:`Manufacturing app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Planning` heading, tick the checkbox for :guilabel:`Security "
"Lead Time`."
msgstr ""
"*Varnostni dobavni rok za proizvodnjo* je nastavljen globalno za podjetje v "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija za proizvodnjo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. "
"Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Načrtovanje` označite potrditveno polje za "
":guilabel:`Varnostni dobavni rok`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:337
msgid ""
"Next, enter the desired number of calendar days. By configuring the security "
"lead time, a buffer is set to account for potential delays in the "
"manufacturing process. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite želeno število koledarskih dni. S konfiguracijo varnostnega "
"dobavnega roka nastavite blažilnik za morebitne zamude v proizvodnem "
"procesu. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the security lead time for manufacturing from the manufacturing app "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Pogled varnostnega dobavnega roka za proizvodnjo iz nastavitev aplikacije za "
"proizvodnjo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:344
msgid ""
"A product has a scheduled shipment date on the :abbr:`DO (Delivery Order)` "
"set for August 15th. The manufacturing lead time is 7 days, and "
"manufacturing security lead time is 3 days. So, the :guilabel:`Scheduled "
"Date` on the |MO| reflects the latest date to begin the manufacturing order. "
"In this example, the planned date on the |MO| is August 5th."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima načrtovan datum odpreme na :abbr:`DO (Dobavnica)`, nastavljen na "
"15. avgust. Dobavna roka proizvodnje je 7 dni, varnostna dobavna roka "
"proizvodnje pa 3 dni. Tako :guilabel:`Načrtovani datum` na |MO| odraža "
"zadnji datum za začetek proizvodnega naloga. V tem primeru je načrtovani "
"datum na |MO| 5. avgust."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:350
msgid "Global example"
msgstr "Splošni primer"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:352
msgid ""
"See the following example to understand how all the lead times work together "
"to ensure timely order fulfillment:"
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si naslednji primer za razumevanje, kako vsi dobavni roki delujejo "
"skupaj za zagotovitev pravočasne izpolnitve naročila:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:355
msgid "**Sales security lead time**: 1 day"
msgstr "**Varnostni dobavni rok prodaje**: 1 dan"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:356
msgid "**Manufacturing security lead time**: 2 days"
msgstr "**Varnostni dobavni rok za proizvodnjo**: 2 dneva"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:357
msgid "**Manufacturing lead time**: 3 days"
msgstr "**Proizvodni dobavni rok**: 3 dni"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:358
msgid "**Purchase security lead time**: 1 day"
msgstr "**Varnostni dobavni rok za nakup**: 1 dan"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:359
msgid "**Vendor lead time**: 4 days"
msgstr "**Dobavni rok dobavitelja**: 4 dni"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:361
msgid ""
"The customer places an order for a manufactured product on September 1st, "
"and the scheduled delivery date from the warehouse is on September 20th. "
"Odoo uses lead times and automated reordering rules to schedule the "
"necessary operations, based on the outgoing shipment delivery date, "
"September 20th:"
msgstr ""
"Stranka odda naročilo za proizveden izdelek 1. septembra in načrtovani datum "
"dobave iz skladišča je 20. september. Odoo uporablja dobavne roke in pravila "
"samodejnega ponovnega naročanja za načrtovanje potrebnih operacij na podlagi "
"datuma dobave izhodne pošiljke, 20. september:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid ""
"Show timeline of how lead times work together to schedule warehouse "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži časovnico, kako dobavni roki delujejo skupaj za načrtovanje "
"skladiščnih operacij."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:368
msgid "**September 1st**: Sales order created, confirmed by salesperson."
msgstr ""
"**1. september**: Prodajni nalog ustvarjen, potrjen s strani prodajalca."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:370
msgid ""
"**September 9th**: Deadline to order components to ensure they arrive in "
"time when manufacturing begins (4-day supplier lead time)."
msgstr ""
"**9. september**: Rok za naročilo komponent, da zagotovimo, da prispejo "
"pravočasno, ko se proizvodnja začne (4-dnevni dobavni rok dobavitelja)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:373
msgid ""
"**September 13th**: Scheduled date of receipt for components. Initially, it "
"was set to 9/14, but the 1-day purchase security lead time pushed the date "
"earlier by 1 day."
msgstr ""
"**13. september**: Načrtovani datum prejema komponent. Sprva je bil "
"nastavljen na 14. 9., vendar je 1-dnevni varnostni dobavni rok za nakup "
"datum prestavil za 1 dan naprej."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:376
msgid ""
"**September 14th**: Deadline to begin manufacturing. Calculated by "
"subtracting the manufacturing lead time of 3 days, and the manufacturing "
"security lead time of 2 days, from the expected delivery date of September "
"19th."
msgstr ""
"**14. september**: Rok za začetek proizvodnje. Izračunan z odštevanjem "
"proizvodnega dobavnega roka 3 dni in varnostnega dobavnega roka za "
"proizvodnjo 2 dni od pričakovanega datuma dobave 19. septembra."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:380
msgid ""
"**September 19th**: :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` on the delivery order form "
"indicates the updated expected delivery date, which was originally set as "
"September 20th. But the sales security lead time pushed the date forward by "
"a day."
msgstr ""
"**19. september**: :guilabel:`Načrtovani datum` na obrazcu dobavnega naloga "
"označuje posodobljen pričakovani datum dobave, ki je bil prvotno nastavljen "
"kot 20. september. Vendar je varnostni dobavni rok za prodajo datum "
"prestavil za dan naprej."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:384
msgid ""
"Odoo's replenishment planning maps a business' order fulfillment process, "
"setting pre-determined deadlines and raw material order dates, including "
"buffer days for potential delays. This ensures products are delivered on "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Odoovo načrtovanje dopolnjevanja prikazuje poslovni proces izpolnjevanja "
"naročil, pri čemer določa vnaprej dogovorjene roke in datume naročila "
"surovin, vključno z rezervnimi dnevi za morebitne zamude. To zagotavlja "
"pravočasno dostavo izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:3
msgid "Replenish on order (MTO)"
msgstr "Dopolnjevanje ob naročilu (MTO)"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:13
msgid ""
"*Replenish on order*, also known as *MTO* (make to order), is a "
"replenishment strategy that creates a draft order every time a product is "
"needed to fulfill a sales order (SO) or as a component in a manufacturing "
"order (MO)."
msgstr ""
"*Dopolnjevanje ob naročilu*, znano tudi kot *MTO* (make to order), je "
"strategija dopolnjevanja, ki ustvari osnutek naročila vsakič, ko je izdelek "
"potreben za izpolnitev prodajnega naloga (SO) ali kot komponenta v "
"proizvodnem nalogu (MO)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:17
msgid ""
"For :doc:`purchased products <../../../purchase/manage_deals/rfq>`, Odoo "
"creates an |RFQ|"
msgstr ""
"Za :doc:`kupljene izdelke <../../../purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` Odoo ustvari "
"|RFQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:18
msgid ""
"For :doc:`manufactured products <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/"
"configure_manufacturing_product>`, it creates an |MO|"
msgstr ""
"Za :doc:`proizvedene izdelke <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/"
"configure_manufacturing_product>` ustvari |MO|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:21
msgid ""
"If stock is available, no |RFQ| or |MO| is generated and the sale proceeds "
"normally. Otherwise, the |RFQ| or |MO| is generated and directly linked to "
"the originating |SO| through a smart button."
msgstr ""
"Če je zaloga na voljo, se |RFQ| ali |MO| ne ustvari in prodaja poteka "
"normalno. V nasprotnem primeru se ustvari |RFQ| ali |MO| in je neposredno "
"povezan z izvornim |SO| prek pametnega gumba."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:24
msgid ""
"This approach offers clear traceability, since each |RFQ| or |MO| is tied "
"back to its demand."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristop ponuja jasno sledljivost, saj je vsak |RFQ| ali |MO| povezan "
"nazaj na njegovo povpraševanje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:27
msgid ""
"The |RFQ| or |MO| generated by |MTO| is designed to fulfill the originating |"
"SO|. These documents should normally be confirmed or adjusted rather than "
"cancelled. If the demand changes, update the document instead of cancelling "
"it."
msgstr ""
"|RFQ| ali |MO|, ki ga ustvari |MTO|, je zasnovan za izpolnitev izvorne |SO|. "
"Te dokumente je treba običajno potrditi ali prilagoditi, ne pa preklicati. "
"Če se povpraševanje spremeni, posodobite dokument namesto da ga prekličete."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:32
msgid ""
"If an |RFQ| or |MO| is cancelled, Odoo does not automatically generate a "
"replacement. A new replenishment document must be created manually, but it "
"**cannot** be linked back to the original |SO| through the smart button."
msgstr ""
"Če je |RFQ| ali |MO| preklican, Odoo samodejno ne ustvari nadomestka. Nov "
"dokument za dopolnitev je treba ustvariti ročno, vendar ga **ni mogoče** "
"povezati nazaj na izvirni |SO| prek pametnega gumba."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:36
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Save` to save the change."
msgstr "Nazadnje kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da shranite spremembo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:41
msgid "Unarchive MTO route"
msgstr "Razarhiviraj pot MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:43
msgid ""
"In order to use the |MTO| route, the :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes` feature "
"must be enabled. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and tick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Multi-"
"Step Routes`, under the :guilabel:`Warehouse` heading."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo poti |MTO| mora biti omogočena funkcija :guilabel:`Večstopenjske "
"poti`. Za to pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Zaloga --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in označite potrditveno polje ob "
":guilabel:`Večstopenjske poti` pod naslovom :guilabel:`Skladišče`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:47
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo sets the |MTO| route as *archived*. This is because |MTO| "
"is a somewhat niche workflow that is only used by certain companies. "
"However, it is easy to unarchive the route in just a few simple steps."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto Odoo nastavi pot |MTO| kot *arhivirano*. To je zato, ker je |MTO| "
"nekoliko nišni potek dela, ki ga uporabljajo samo določena podjetja. Vendar "
"je pot enostavno razarhivirati v le nekaj preprostih korakih."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:51
msgid ""
"To do so, begin by navigating to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Routes`. On the :guilabel:`Routes` page, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(down arrow)` icon on the right side of "
"the search bar, and click the :guilabel:`Archived` filter to enable it."
msgstr ""
"Za to najprej pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Zaloga --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Poti`. Na strani :guilabel:`Poti` kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` :guilabel:`(puščica navzdol)` na desni strani iskalne vrstice in "
"kliknite filter :guilabel:`Arhivirano`, da ga omogočite."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:None
msgid "The archived filter on the Routes page."
msgstr "Filter arhivirano na strani Poti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:59
msgid ""
"After enabling the :guilabel:`Archived` filter, the :guilabel:`Routes` page "
"shows all routes which are currently archived. Tick the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Replenish on Order (MTO)`, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button to reveal a drop-down menu. From the drop-"
"down menu, select :guilabel:`Unarchive`."
msgstr ""
"Po omogočitvi filtra :guilabel:`Arhivirano` stran :guilabel:`Poti` prikaže "
"vse poti, ki so trenutno arhivirane. Označite potrditveno polje ob "
":guilabel:`Dopolni ob naročilu (MTO)`, nato kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanja`, da razkrijete spustni meni. Iz spustnega menija "
"izberite :guilabel:`Razarhiviraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:None
msgid "The unarchive action on the Routes page."
msgstr "Dejanje razarhiviranja na strani Poti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:68
msgid ""
"Finally, remove the :guilabel:`Archived` filter from the search bar. "
"The :guilabel:`Routes` page now shows all unarchived routes, "
"including :guilabel:`Replenish on Order (MTO)`, which is selectable on the "
"*Inventory* tab of each product page."
msgstr ""
"Končno odstranite filter :guilabel:`Arhivirano` iz iskalne vrstice. Stran "
":guilabel:`Poti` zdaj prikaže vse nearhivirane poti, vključno z "
":guilabel:`Dopolni ob naročilu (MTO)`, ki je izbran na zavihku *Zaloga* na "
"strani vsakega izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:73
msgid "Configure product for MTO"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj izdelek za MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:75
msgid ""
"With the |MTO| route unarchived, products can now be properly configured to "
"use replenish on order. To do so, begin by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Products`, then select an "
"existing product, or click :guilabel:`New` to configure a new one."
msgstr ""
"Ko je pot |MTO| razarhivirana, je izdelke zdaj mogoče pravilno konfigurirati "
"za uporabo dopolnjevanja ob naročilu. Za to najprej pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Zaloga --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`, nato izberite "
"obstoječi izdelek ali kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da konfigurirate novega."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:79
msgid ""
"On the product page, select the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Replenish on Order (MTO)` route in the :guilabel:`Routes` "
"section, along with the :guilabel:`Buy` or :guilabel:`Manufacture` route."
msgstr ""
"Na strani izdelka izberite zavihek :guilabel:`Zaloga` in omogočite pot "
":guilabel:`Dopolni ob naročilu (MTO)` v razdelku :guilabel:`Poti` skupaj s "
"potjo :guilabel:`Kupi` ali :guilabel:`Proizvedi`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:84
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Replenish on Order (MTO)` route **does not** work unless "
"another route is selected as well. This is because Odoo needs to know how to "
"replenish the product when an order is placed for it (buy or manufacture it)."
msgstr ""
"Pot :guilabel:`Dopolni ob naročilu (MTO)` **ne** deluje, če ni izbrana tudi "
"druga pot. To je zato, ker mora Odoo vedeti, kako dopolniti izdelek, ko je "
"zanj oddano naročilo (kupiti ali proizvesti ga)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:None
msgid "Select the MTO route and a second route on the Inventory tab."
msgstr "Na zavihku Zaloga izberite pot MTO in drugo pot."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:92
msgid ""
"If the product is purchased from a vendor to fulfill |SOs|, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Can be Purchased` checkbox under the product name. Doing so "
"makes the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab appear alongside the other tabs below."
msgstr ""
"Če se izdelek kupi od dobavitelja za izpolnitev |SOs|, omogočite potrditveno "
"polje :guilabel:`Mogoče kupiti` pod imenom izdelka. S tem se "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Nakup` prikaže skupaj z drugimi zavihki spodaj."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:96
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab and specify a :guilabel:`Vendor` and "
"the :guilabel:`Price` they sell the product for."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Nakup` in določite :guilabel:`Dobavitelj` "
"ter :guilabel:`Cena`, po kateri prodaja izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:100
msgid ""
"Specifying a vendor is essential for this workflow, because Odoo cannot "
"generate an |RFQ| without knowing who the product is purchased from."
msgstr ""
"Določitev dobavitelja je bistvena za ta potek dela, ker Odoo ne more "
"ustvariti |RFQ|, ne da bi vedel, od koga se izdelek kupuje."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the product is manufactured, make sure it has a bill of materials (BOM) "
"configured for it. To do so, click the :guilabel:`Bill of Materials` smart "
"button at the top of the screen, then click :guilabel:`New` on "
"the :guilabel:`Bill of Materials` page to configure a new |BOM| for the "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Če se izdelek proizvaja, se prepričajte, da ima konfiguriran kosovni seznam "
"(BOM). To storite tako, da kliknete pametni gumb :guilabel:`Kosovni seznam` "
"na vrhu zaslona, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` na strani :guilabel:`Kosovni "
"seznam`, da konfigurirate nov |BOM| za izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:108
msgid ""
"For a full overview of |BOM| creation, see the documentation on :doc:`bills "
"of materials <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/bill_configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Za celovit pregled ustvarjanja |BOM| si oglejte dokumentacijo "
"o :doc:`kosovnih seznamih <../../../manufacturing/basic_setup/"
"bill_configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:112
msgid "Replenish using MTO"
msgstr "Dopolnjevanje z uporabo MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:114
msgid ""
"After configuring a product to use the |MTO| route, a replenishment order is "
"created for it every time an |SO| or |MO| including the product is "
"confirmed. The type of order created depends on the second route selected in "
"addition to |MTO|."
msgstr ""
"Po konfiguraciji izdelka za uporabo poti |MTO| se zanj ustvari naročilo za "
"dopolnjevanje vsakič, ko je potrjen |SO| ali |MO|, ki vključuje izdelek. "
"Vrsta ustvarjenega naročila je odvisna od druge poti, izbrane poleg |MTO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:118
msgid ""
"For example, if *Buy* was the second route selected, then a |PO| is created "
"upon confirmation of an |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če je bila kot druga pot izbrana *Nakup*, se ob potrditvi |SO| "
"ustvari |PO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:122
msgid ""
"When the |MTO| route is enabled for a product, a replenishment order is "
"always created upon confirmation of an |SO| or |MO|. This is the case, even "
"if there is enough stock of the product on-hand to fulfill the |SO|, without "
"buying or manufacturing additional units of it."
msgstr ""
"Ko je za izdelek omogočena pot |MTO|, se ob potrditvi |SO| ali |MO| vedno "
"ustvari naročilo za dopolnjevanje. To velja tudi, če je na zalogi dovolj "
"izdelka za izpolnitev |SO|, ne da bi bilo treba kupiti ali proizvesti "
"dodatne enote."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:126
msgid ""
"While the |MTO| route can be used in unison with the *Buy* or *Manufacture* "
"routes, the *Buy* route is used as the example for this workflow. Begin by "
"navigating to the :menuselection:`Sales` app, then click :guilabel:`New`, "
"which opens a blank quotation form."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav se pot |MTO| lahko uporablja skupaj s potema *Nakup* ali "
"*Proizvodnja*, se v tem poteku dela kot primer uporablja pot *Nakup*. "
"Začnite tako, da se pomaknete do aplikacije :menuselection:`Prodaja`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, kar odpre prazen obrazec za ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:130
msgid ""
"On the blank quotation form, add a :guilabel:`Customer`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a product` under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and "
"enter a product configured to use the *MTO* and *Buy* routes. "
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm`, and the quotation is turned into an |SO|."
msgstr ""
"V praznem obrazcu za ponudbo dodajte :guilabel:`Kupec`. Nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj izdelek` pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila` "
"in vnesite izdelek, konfiguriran za uporabo poti *MTO* in *Nakup*. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi` in ponudba se spremeni v |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:134
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Purchase` smart button now appears at the top of the page. "
"Clicking it opens the |RFQ| associated with the |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu strani se prikaže pametni gumb :guilabel:`Nakup`. Klik nanj odpre |"
"RFQ|, povezan z |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:137
msgid ""
"After receiving approval from the vendor that they can meet the demand by "
"the :guilabel:`Expected Arrival` date, click :guilabel:`Confirm Order` to "
"turn it into a |PO|. A purple :guilabel:`Receive Products` button now "
"appears above the |PO|. Once the products are received, "
"click :guilabel:`Receive Products` to open the receipt order, and "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to enter the products into inventory."
msgstr ""
"Potem ko prejmete potrditev dobavitelja, da lahko izpolni povpraševanje do "
"datuma :guilabel:`Pričakovani prihod`, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi naročilo`, "
"da ga spremenite v |PO|. Nad |PO| se sedaj prikaže vijoličen "
"gumb :guilabel:`Prejmi izdelke`. Ko so izdelki prejeti, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Prejmi izdelke`, da odprete prejemnico, in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da vnesete izdelke v zalogo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:143
msgid ""
"Return to the |SO| by clicking the :guilabel:`SO` breadcrumb, or by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Orders`, and "
"selecting the |SO|."
msgstr ""
"Vrnite se na |SO| s klikom na breadcrumb :guilabel:`SO` ali z navigacijo "
"do :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Naročila --> Naročila` in izberite "
"|SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:146
msgid ""
"Finally, click the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button at the top of the order "
"to open the delivery order. Once the products have been shipped to the "
"customer, click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Dostava` na vrhu naročila, da "
"odprete nalog za dostavo. Ko so izdelki odpremljeni kupcu, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da potrdite dostavo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:151
msgid "Cancelling an SO with an MTO product"
msgstr "Preklic prodajnega naloga z izdelkom MTO"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:153
msgid ""
"When a |SO| is cancelled, and it had created an |RFQ| or |MO|, the related "
"delivery order is cancelled automatically. However, the |RFQ| or |MO| "
"themselves are **not** cancelled. Instead, a warning appears in their "
"chatter noting the |SO| cancellation. These documents remain active, so the "
"user can either cancel them manually or repurpose the replenishment for "
"another order."
msgstr ""
"Ko je |SO| preklican in je ustvaril |RFQ| ali |MO|, se povezano dobavno "
"naročilo samodejno prekliče. Vendar pa |RFQ| ali |MO| sama **nista** "
"preklicana. Namesto tega se v njunem pogovornem oknu pojavi opozorilo, ki "
"opaža preklic |SO|. Ti dokumenti ostanejo aktivni, zato lahko uporabnik ali "
"ročno prekliče ali pa dopolnitev znova nameni drugemu naročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/mto.rst:159
msgid ""
"For information on workflows that include the |MTO| route, see the following "
"documentation:"
msgstr ""
"Za informacije o poteh dela, ki vključujejo pot |MTO|, glejte naslednjo "
"dokumentacijo:"

