msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number`: specifies the lot or serial number of the "
"tracked product being moved."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Številka serije/lot`: določa številko serije ali lote sljedenega "
"izdelka, ki se premika."

